# <a name="sensitive-information-type-entity-definitions"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-104">Определения типов конфиденциальной информации</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-104">Sensitive information type entity definitions</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-105">В этой статье перечислены все определения типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-105">This article lists all sensitive information type entity definitions.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-106">Каждое определение показывает, что политика DLP ищет для обнаружения каждого типа.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-106">Each definition shows what a DLP policy looks for to detect each type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-107">Дополнительные сведения о типах конфиденциальной информации см. [в](sensitive-information-type-learn-about.md)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-107">To learn more about sensitive information types, see [Sensitive information types](sensitive-information-type-learn-about.md)</span></span>

## <a name="aba-routing-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-108">Номер маршрутивки ABA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-108">ABA routing number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-109">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-109">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-110">девять цифр, которые могут быть в форматированном или неформатированном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-110">nine digits that may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-111">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-111">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-112">две цифры в диапазонах 00-12, 21-32, 61-72 или 80</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-112">two digits in the ranges 00-12, 21-32, 61-72, or 80</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-113">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-113">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-114">необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-114">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-115">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-115">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-116">необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-116">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-117">цифру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-117">a digit</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-118">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-118">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-119">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-119">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-120">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-120">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-121">Политика имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-121">A policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-122">функция Func_aba_routing находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-122">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-123">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ABA_Routing.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-123">A keyword from Keyword_ABA_Routing is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-124">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-124">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-125">функция Func_aba_routing находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-125">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- ABA Routing Number -->
    <Entity id="cb353f78-2b72-4c3c-8827-92ebe4f69fdf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ABA_Routing" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="argentina-national-identity-dni-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-143">Номер национального удостоверения (DNI) Аргентины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-143">Argentina national identity (DNI) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-144">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-144">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-145">Восемь цифр с периодами или без них</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-145">Eight digits with or without periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-146">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-146">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-147">Восемь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-147">Eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-148">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-148">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-149">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-149">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-150">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-150">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-151">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-151">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-152">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-152">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-153">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-153">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-154">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-154">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-155">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-155">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-156">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-156">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-157">регулярное выражение Regex_argentina_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-157">The regular expression Regex_argentina_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-158">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_argentina_national_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-158">A keyword from Keyword_argentina_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Argentina National Identity (DNI) Number -->
<Entity id="eefbb00e-8282-433c-8620-8f1da3bffdb2" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_argentina_national_id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_argentina_national_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_argentina_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-160">Keyword_argentina_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-160">Keyword_argentina_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-161">Argentina National Identity number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-161">Argentina National Identity number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-163">cédula</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-163">cédula</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-164">dni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-164">dni</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-165">documento nacional de identidad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-165">documento nacional de identidad</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-166">documento número</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-166">documento número</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-167">нумеро documento</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-167">documento numero</span></span>

## <a name="argentina-unique-tax-identification-key-cuitcuil"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-170">Уникальный ключ идентификации налогов в Аргентине (CUIT/CUIL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-170">Argentina Unique Tax Identification Key (CUIT/CUIL)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-171">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-171">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-172">11 цифр с тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-172">11 digits with dash</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-173">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-173">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-174">11 цифр с тире:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-174">11 digits with a dash:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-175">две цифры в 20, 23, 24, 27, 30, 33 или 34</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-175">two digits in 20, 23, 24, 27, 30, 33 or 34</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-176">дефис (-)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-176">a hyphen (-)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-177">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-177">eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-178">дефис (-)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-178">a hyphen (-)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-179">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-179">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-180">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-180">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-181">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-181">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-182">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-182">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-183">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-183">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-184">Функция находит `Func_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-184">The function `Func_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-185">Найдено ключевое `Keyword_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-185">A keyword from `Keyword_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-186">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-186">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-187">Функция находит `Func_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-187">The function `Func_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- Argentina Unique Tax Identification Key (CUIT/CUIL) -->
      <Entity id="98da3da1-9199-4571-b7c4-b6522980b507" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-188">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-188">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_argentina_unique_tax_key"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-189">Keyword_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-189">Keyword_Argentina_Unique_Tax_Key</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-190">Clave Unica de Identificacion Tributaria</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-190">Clave Unica de Identificacion Tributaria</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-191">CUIT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-191">CUIT</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-192">уникальный код идентификации труда</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-192">unique code of labour identification</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-193">Clave Única de Identificación Tributaria</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-193">Clave Única de Identificación Tributaria</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-194">уникальный код идентификации труда</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-194">unique labour identification code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-195">CUIL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-195">CUIL</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-196">Уникальный ключ идентификации налогов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-196">Unique Tax Identification Key</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-197">Уникальный ключ идентификации рабочей силы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-197">Unique Labour Identification Key</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-198">Уникальный ключ идентификации труда</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-198">Unique Key of Labour Identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-199">Уникальный код идентификации работы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-199">Unique Work Identification Code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-200">Уникальный код идентификации работы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-200">Unique Code of Work Identification</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-202">Уникальный ключ идентификации работы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-202">Unique Key of Work Identification</span></span>

## <a name="australia-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-226">Номер банковского счета в Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-226">Australia bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-227">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-227">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-228">от шести до 10 цифр с номером филиала банковского филиала или без него</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-228">six to 10 digits with or without a bank state branch number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-229">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-229">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-230">Номер учетной записи — от 6 до 10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-230">Account number is 6 to 10 digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-231">Номер филиала государственного банка Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-231">Australia bank state branch number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-232">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-232">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-233">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-233">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-234">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-234">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-235">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-235">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-236">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-236">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-237">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-237">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-238">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-238">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-239">Обычное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-239">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-240">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-240">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-241">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-241">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-242">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-242">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-243">Обычное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-243">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-244">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-244">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="74a54de9-2a30-4aa0-a8aa-3d9327fc07c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb" />
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
  </Pattern>
 </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_australia_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-246">Keyword_australia_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-246">Keyword_australia_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-252">bank address</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-252">bank address</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-253">information account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-253">information account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-255">bank charges</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-255">bank charges</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-256">bank details</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-256">bank details</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-257">banking information</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-257">banking information</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-258">full names</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-258">full names</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-259">магатэ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-259">iaea</span></span>

## <a name="australia-business-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-260">Номер бизнеса в Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-260">Australia business number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-261">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-261">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-262">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-262">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-263">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-263">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-264">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-264">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-265">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-265">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-266">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-266">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-267">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-267">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-268">11 цифр с необязательными делимитерами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-268">11 digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-269">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-269">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-270">11 цифр с необязательными делимитерами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-270">11 digits with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-271">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-271">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-272">необязательный дефис или пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-272">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-273">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-273">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-274">необязательный дефис или пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-274">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-275">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-275">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-276">необязательный дефис или пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-276">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-277">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-277">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-278">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-278">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-279">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-279">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-280">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-280">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-281">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-281">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-282">Функция Func_australian_business_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-282">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-283">Ключевое слово Keywords_australian_business_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-283">A keyword from Keywords_australian_business_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-284">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-284">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-285">Функция Func_australian_business_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-285">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Business Number -->
      <Entity id="76e83b3b-01ee-4530-aced-e667a6609f49" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_australia_business_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-287">Keyword_australia_business_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-287">Keyword_australia_business_number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-296">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-296">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-297">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-297">data loss prevention policies</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-302">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-302">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-303">девять цифр с делимитерами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-303">nine digits with delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-304">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-304">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-305">девять цифр с делимитерами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-305">nine digits with delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-306">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-306">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-307">пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-307">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-308">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-308">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-309">пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-309">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-310">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-310">three digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-311">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-311">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-312">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-312">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-313">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-313">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-314">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-314">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-315">Функция Func_Australian_Company_Number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-315">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-316">Ключевое слово Keyword_Australian_Company_Number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-316">A keyword from Keyword_Australian_Company_Number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-317">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-317">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-318">Функция Func_Australian_Company_Number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-318">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Company Number -->
      <Entity id="b1fba4f7-7b3e-4bb9-8f9a-9366df604dbb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-323">Австралийская компания нет #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-323">australia company no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-324">Номер австралийской компании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-324">australia company number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-326">Австралийская компания нет #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-326">australian company no#</span></span>

## <a name="australia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-328">Номер лицензии водителя в Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-328">Australia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-329">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-329">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-330">девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-330">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-331">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-331">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-332">девять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-332">nine letters and digits:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-333">две цифры или буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-333">two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-334">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-334">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-335">пять цифр или букв (не чувствительных к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-335">five digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-336">ИЛИ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-336">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-337">от одного до двух необязательных букв (не чувствительных к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-337">one to two optional letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-338">четыре-девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-338">four to nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-339">ИЛИ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-339">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-340">девять цифр или букв (не чувствительных к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-340">nine digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-341">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-341">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-342">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-342">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-343">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-343">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-344">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-344">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-345">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-345">The regular expression Regex_australia_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-346">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-346">A keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-347">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-347">No keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Drivers License Number -->
<Entity id="1cbbc8f5-9216-4392-9eb5-5ac2298d1356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-medical-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-447">Номер медицинской учетной записи Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-447">Australia medical account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-448">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-448">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-449">10–11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-449">10-11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-450">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-450">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-451">10–11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-451">10-11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-452">Первая цифра находится в диапазоне 2–6.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-452">First digit is in the range 2-6</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-453">Девятая цифра — проверочная.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-453">Ninth digit is a check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-454">Десятая цифра — цифра серии.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-454">Tenth digit is the issue digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-455">Одиннадцатая цифра (необязательно) — индивидуальный номер.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-455">Eleventh digit (optional) is the individual number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-456">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-456">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-457">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-457">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-458">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-458">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-459">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-459">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-460">функция Func_australian_medical_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-460">The function Func_australian_medical_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-461">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-461">A keyword from Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-462">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-462">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
  <!-- Australia Medical Account Number -->
<Entity id="104a99a0-3d3b-4542-a40d-ab0b9e1efe63" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_medical_account_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number"/>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-463">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-463">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_australia_medical_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-464">Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-464">Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-465">bank account details</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-465">bank account details</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-466">medicare payments</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-466">medicare payments</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-467">mortgage account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-467">mortgage account</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-468">bank payments</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-468">bank payments</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-469">information branch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-469">information branch</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-470">credit card loan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-470">credit card loan</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-471">department of human services</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-471">department of human services</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-472">local service</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-472">local service</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-473">medicare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-473">medicare</span></span>

   
## <a name="australia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-474">Номер паспорта Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-474">Australia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-475">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-475">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-476">восемь или девять символов альфа-цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-476">eight or nine alphanumeric characters</span></span> 

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-477">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-477">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-478">одна буква (N, E, D, F, A, C, U, X) с семью цифрами или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-478">one letter (N, E, D, F, A, C, U, X) followed by seven digits or</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-479">Две буквы (PA, PB, PC, PD, PE, PF, PU, PW, PX, PZ) с семью цифрами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-479">Two letters (PA, PB, PC, PD, PE, PF, PU, PW, PX, PZ) followed by seven digits.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-480">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-480">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-481">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-481">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-482">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-482">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-483">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-483">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-484">Обычное выражение `Regex_australia_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-484">The regular expression `Regex_australia_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-485">Найдено ключевое `Keyword_australia_passport_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-485">A keyword from `Keyword_australia_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-486">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-486">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-487">Обычное выражение `Regex_australia_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-487">The regular expression `Regex_australia_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- Australia Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="29869db6-602d-4853-ab93-3484f905df50" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_passport_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>  
```

## <a name="australia-tax-file-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-507">Номер налогового файла Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-507">Australia tax file number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-508">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-508">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-509">восемь-девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-509">eight to nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-510">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-510">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-511">от восьми до девяти цифр, обычно представленных с пробелами следующим образом:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-511">eight to nine digits typically presented with spaces as follows:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-512">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-512">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-513">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-513">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-514">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-514">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-515">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-515">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-516">две-три цифры, где последняя цифра — это контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-516">two to three digits where the last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-517">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-517">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-518">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-518">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-519">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-519">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-520">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-520">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-521">функция Func_australian_tax_file_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-521">The function Func_australian_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-522">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number или Keyword_number_exclusions не найдено;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-522">No keyword from Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number or Keyword_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-523">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-523">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
   <!-- Australia Tax File Number -->
    <Entity id="e29bc95f-ff70-4a37-aa01-04d17360a4c5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_tax_file_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-524">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-524">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_australia_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-525">Keyword_australia_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-525">Keyword_australia_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-528">medicare levy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-528">medicare levy</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-529">portfolio number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-529">portfolio number</span></span>

## <a name="austria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-535">Номер водительских прав в Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-535">Austria driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-536">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-536">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-537">восемь цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-537">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-538">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-538">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-539">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-539">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-540">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-540">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-541">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-541">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-542">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-542">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-543">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-543">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-544">Обычное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-544">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-545">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-545">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="682f18ce-44eb-482b-8198-2bcb96a0761e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-672">Удостоверение личности в Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-672">Austria identity card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-673">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-673">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-674">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-674">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-675">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-675">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-676">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-676">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-677">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-677">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-678">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-678">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-679">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-679">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-680">Сочетание букв, цифр и специальных символов с 24 символами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-680">A 24-character combination of letters, digits, and special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-681">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-681">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-682">24 символа:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-682">24 characters:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-683">22 буквы (не чувствительные к делу), цифры, задние ресницы, косые черты или знаки плюс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-683">22 letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, or plus signs</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-684">две буквы (не чувствительные к делу), цифры, backslashes, перенаправляющие черты, плюс знаки или равные знаки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-684">two letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, plus signs, or equal signs</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-685">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-685">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-686">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-686">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-687">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-687">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-688">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-688">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-689">Обычное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-689">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-690">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-690">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
   
```xml
      <!-- Austria Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="5ec06c3b-007e-4820-8343-7ff73b889735" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-691">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-691">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-692">Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-692">Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-693">номер удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-693">identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-694">national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-694">national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-695">personalausweis republik österreich</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-695">personalausweis republik österreich</span></span>

## <a name="austria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-696">Номер паспорта Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-696">Austria passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-697">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-697">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-698">Одна буква с необязательным пространством и семью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-698">One letter followed by an optional space and seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-699">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-699">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-700">Сочетание одной буквы, семи цифр и одного пространства:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-700">A combination of one letter, seven digits, and one space:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-701">одна буква (не деликатная)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-701">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-702">одно пространство (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-702">one space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-703">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-703">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-704">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-704">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-705">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-705">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-706">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-706">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-707">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-707">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-708">Обычное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-708">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-709">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-709">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-710">Обычное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате DD.MM.YYYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-710">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-711">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-711">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-712">Обычное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-712">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-713">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-713">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1c96ae4e-303b-447d-86c7-77113ac266bf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-715">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-715">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-723">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-723">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-724">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-724">passportnumbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-726">Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-726">Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-727">reisepassnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-727">reisepassnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-728">reisepasse</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-728">reisepasse</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-729">No-Reisepass</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-729">No-Reisepass</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-730">Nr-Reisepass</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-730">Nr-Reisepass</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-732">Passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-732">Passnummer</span></span>

## <a name="austria-social-security-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-737">Номер социального обеспечения в Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-737">Austria social security number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-738">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-738">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-739">10 цифр в указанном формате</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-739">10 digits in the specified format</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-740">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-740">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-741">10 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-741">10 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-742">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-742">three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-743">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-743">one check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-744">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (DDMMYY)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-744">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-745">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-745">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-746">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-746">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-747">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-747">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-748">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-748">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-749">Функция находит  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-749">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-750">найдено  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` ключевое слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-750">a keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-751">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-751">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-752">Функция находит  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-752">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Social Security Number -->
      <Entity id="6896a906-86c9-4d19-a2da-6e43ccd19b7b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-753">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-753">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-754">Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-754">Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-755">austrian ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-755">austrian ssn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-756">номер ehic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-756">ehic number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-757">ehic нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-757">ehic no</span></span>

## <a name="austria-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-778">Идентификационный номер налога в Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-778">Austria tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-779">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-779">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-780">девять цифр с необязательными чертами дефиза и вперед</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-780">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-781">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-781">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-782">девять цифр с необязательными чертами дефиза и вперед:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-782">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-783">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-783">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-784">дефис (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-784">a hyphen (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-785">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-785">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-786">косая черта (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-786">a forward slash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-787">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-787">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-788">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-788">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-789">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-789">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-790">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-790">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-791">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-791">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-792">Функция находит  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-792">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-793">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-793">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-794">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-794">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-795">Функция находит  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-795">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="4fd58d22-af28-4451-b18a-6f722430a56d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-807">номер регистрации налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-807">tax registration number</span></span>

## <a name="austria-value-added-tax"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-818">Налог на добавленную стоимость в Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-818">Austria value added tax</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-819">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-819">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-820">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-820">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-821">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-821">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-822">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-822">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-823">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-823">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-824">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-824">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-825">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-825">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-826">Альфанумерный шаблон с 11-символами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-826">11-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-827">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-827">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-828">11-символ альфанумерного шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-828">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-829">A или a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-829">A or a</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-830">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-830">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-831">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-831">Optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-832">U или u</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-832">U or u</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-833">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-833">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-834">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-834">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-835">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-835">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-836">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-836">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-837">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-837">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-838">одна или две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-838">one or two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-839">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-839">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-840">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-840">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-841">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-841">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-842">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-842">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-843">Функция Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-843">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-844">Ключевое слово Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-844">A keyword from Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-845">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-845">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-846">Функция Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-846">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Austria Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="b6a3eda2-c56c-4b69-a5f7-dca34db00f48" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
