## <a name="azure-documentdb-auth-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-864">Ключ auth Azure DocumentDB</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-864">Azure DocumentDB auth key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-865">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-865">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-866">Строка "DocumentDb" с символами и строками, описанными в приведенной ниже схеме.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-866">The string "DocumentDb" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-867">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-867">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-868">Строка "DocumentDb"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-868">The string "DocumentDb"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-869">Любое сочетание между 3-200 буквами нижнего или верхнего шкафа, цифрами, символами, специальными символами или пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-869">Any combination of between 3-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-870">Больше символа (>), равного знака (=), кавычка (") или apostrophe (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-870">A greater than symbol (>), an equal sign (=), a quotation mark ("), or an apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-871">Любое сочетание из 86 букв нижнего или верхнего шкафа, цифр, переназначений (/) или знака плюс (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-871">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-872">Два одинаковых знака (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-872">Two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-873">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-873">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-874">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-874">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-875">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-875">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-876">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-876">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-877">Обычное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-877">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-878">Обычное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-878">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Azure Document DB Auth Key -->
<Entity id="0f587d92-eb28-44a9-bd1c-90f2892b47aa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
          </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-879">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-879">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-884">northwind</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-884">northwind</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-885">песочница</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-885">sandbox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-886">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-886">onebox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-887">localhost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-887">localhost</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-888">127.0.0.1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-888">127.0.0.1</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-891">s-int.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-891">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-892">net</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-892">net</span></span>

## <a name="azure-iaas-database-connection-string-and-azure-sql-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-893">Строка подключения к базе данных Azure IAAS и строка SQL Azure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-893">Azure IAAS database connection string and Azure SQL connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-894">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-894">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-895">Строка "Server", "server" или "data source" с символами и строками, описанными в приведенном ниже шаблоне, включая строку "cloudapp.azure".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-895">The string "Server", "server", or "data source" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-896">com" или "cloudapp.azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-896">com" or "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-897">net" или "database.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-897">net" or "database.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-898">net", а также строка "Пароль", "пароль" или "pwd".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-898">net", and the string "Password" or "password" or "pwd".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-899">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-899">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-900">строка "Server", "server" или "источник данных"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-900">the string "Server", "server", or "data source"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-901">от нуля до двух символов белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-901">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-902">равный знак (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-902">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-903">от нуля до двух символов белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-903">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-904">любое сочетание между 1-200 буквами нижнего или верхнего шкафа, цифрами, символами, специальными символами или пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-904">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-905">Строка "cloudapp.azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-905">The string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-906">com", "cloudapp.azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-906">com", "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-907">net", или "database.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-907">net", or "database.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-908">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-908">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-909">любое сочетание между 1-300 буквами нижнего или верхнего шкафа, цифрами, символами, специальными символами или пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-909">any combination of between 1-300 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-910">строка "Пароль", "пароль" или "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-910">the string "Password", "password", or "pwd"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-911">от нуля до двух символов белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-911">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-912">равный знак (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-912">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-913">от нуля до двух символов белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-913">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-914">один или несколько символов, которые не являются полуколоном (;), кавычка (") или апостроф (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-914">one or more characters that aren't a semicolon (;), quotation mark ("), or apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-915">полуколон (;), кавычка (") или апостроф (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-915">a semicolon (;), quotation mark ("), or apostrophe (')</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-916">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-916">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-917">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-917">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-918">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-918">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-919">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-919">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-920">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-920">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-921">Обычное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-921">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure IAAS Database Connection String and Azure SQL Connection String-->
<Entity id="ce1a126d-186f-4700-8c0c-486157b953fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-922">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-922">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_common_example_keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-923">CEP_common_example_keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-923">CEP_common_example_keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-924">(Технически этот тип конфиденциальной информации определяет эти ключевые слова с помощью регулярного выражения, а не списка ключевых слов.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-924">(Technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-925">contoso</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-925">contoso</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-926">fabrikam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-926">fabrikam</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-927">northwind</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-927">northwind</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-928">песочница</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-928">sandbox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-929">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-929">onebox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-930">localhost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-930">localhost</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-931">127.0.0.1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-931">127.0.0.1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-932">тесты.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-932">testacs.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-933">com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-933">com</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-934">s-int.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-934">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-935">net</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-935">net</span></span>

## <a name="azure-iot-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-936">Строка подключения к IoT Azure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-936">Azure IoT connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-937">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-937">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-938">Строка "HostName" с символами и строками, описанными в рисунке ниже, включая строки "azure-devices".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-938">The string "HostName" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-939">net" и "SharedAccessKey".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-939">net" and "SharedAccessKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-940">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-940">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-941">строка "HostName"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-941">the string "HostName"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-942">от нуля до двух символов белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-942">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-943">равный знак (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-943">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-944">от нуля до двух символов белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-944">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-945">любое сочетание между 1-200 буквами нижнего или верхнего шкафа, цифрами, символами, специальными символами или пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-945">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-946">строка "azure-devices.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-946">the string "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-947">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-947">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-948">любое сочетание между 1-200 буквами нижнего или верхнего шкафа, цифрами, символами, специальными символами или пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-948">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-949">строка "SharedAccessKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-949">the string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-950">от нуля до двух символов белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-950">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-951">равный знак (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-951">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-952">от нуля до двух символов белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-952">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-953">любое сочетание из 43 букв нижнего или верхнего шкафа, цифр, переназначений (/) или знака плюс (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-953">any combination of 43 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-954">равный знак (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-954">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-955">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-955">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-956">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-956">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-957">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-957">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-958">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-958">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-959">Обычное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-959">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-960">Обычное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-960">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure IoT Connection String-->
<Entity id="0b34bec3-d5d6-4974-b7b0-dcdb5c90c29d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-publish-setting-password"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-975">Пароль параметра публикации Azure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-975">Azure publish setting password</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-976">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-976">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-977">Строка "userpwd=" с последующим альфа-числом строка.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-977">The string "userpwd=" followed by an alphanumeric string.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-978">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-978">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-979">строка "userpwd="</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-979">the string "userpwd="</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-980">любое сочетание из 60 нижних букв или цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-980">any combination of 60 lowercase letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-981">кавычка ()</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-981">a quotation mark (")</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-982">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-982">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-983">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-983">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-984">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-984">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-985">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-985">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-986">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-986">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-987">Обычное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-987">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>


```xml
<!--Azure Publish Setting Password-->
<Entity id="75f4cc8a-a68e-49e5-89ce-fa8f03d286a5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
       <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords" />
       <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
           <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
       </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-995">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-995">onebox</span></span>

## <a name="azure-redis-cache-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1002">Строка подключения кэша Azure Redis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1002">Azure Redis cache connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1003">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1003">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1004">Строка "redis.cache.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1004">The string "redis.cache.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1005">net" с символами и строками, описанными в приведенной ниже схеме, включая строку "пароль" или "pwd".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1005">net" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "password" or "pwd".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1006">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1006">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1007">строка "redis.cache.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1007">the string "redis.cache.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1008">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1008">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1009">любое сочетание между 1-200 буквами нижнего или верхнего шкафа, цифрами, символами, специальными символами или пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1009">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1010">строка "пароль" или "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1010">the string "password" or "pwd"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1011">от нуля до двух символов белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1011">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1012">равный знак (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1012">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1013">от нуля до двух символов белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1013">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1014">любое сочетание из 43 символов, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего шкафа, цифрами, переназначаемой чертой (/) или знаком плюс (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1014">any combination of 43 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1015">равный знак (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1015">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1016">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1016">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1017">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1017">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1018">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1018">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1019">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1019">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1020">Обычное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1020">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1021">Обычное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1021">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Redis Cache Connection String-->
<Entity id="095a7e6c-efd8-46d5-af7b-5298d53a49fc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1029">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1029">onebox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1030">localhost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1030">localhost</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1031">127.0.0.1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1031">127.0.0.1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1032">тесты.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1032">testacs.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1033">com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1033">com</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1034">s-int.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1034">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1035">net</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1035">net</span></span>

## <a name="azure-sas"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1036">Azure SAS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1036">Azure SAS</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1037">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1037">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1038">Строка "sig" с символами и строками, описанными в рисунке ниже.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1038">The string "sig" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1039">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1039">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1040">строка "sig"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1040">the string "sig"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1041">от нуля до двух символов белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1041">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1042">равный знак (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1042">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1043">от нуля до двух символов белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1043">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1044">любое сочетание между 43-53 символами, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего шкафа, цифрами или процентным знаком (%)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1044">any combination of between 43-53 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, or the percent sign (%)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1045">строка "%3d"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1045">the string "%3d"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1046">любой символ, который не является нижней или верхней буквой, цифрой или процентным знаком (%)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1046">any character that isn't a lower- or uppercase letter, digit, or percent sign (%)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1047">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1047">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1048">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1048">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1049">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1049">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1050">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1050">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1051">Обычное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureSAS находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1051">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureSAS finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure SAS-->
<Entity id="4d235014-e564-47f4-a6fb-6ebb4a826834" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureSAS" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-service-bus-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1052">Строка подключения к шинам службы Azure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1052">Azure service bus connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1053">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1053">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1054">Строка "EndPoint", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенной ниже схеме, включая строки "servicebus.windows".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1054">The string "EndPoint" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "servicebus.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1055">net" и "SharedAccesKey".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1055">net" and "SharedAccesKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1056">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1056">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1057">строка "EndPoint"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1057">the string "EndPoint"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1058">от нуля до двух символов белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1058">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1059">равный знак (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1059">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1060">от нуля до двух символов белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1060">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1061">любое сочетание между 1-200 буквами нижнего или верхнего шкафа, цифрами, символами, специальными символами или пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1061">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1062">строка "servicebus.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1062">the string "servicebus.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1063">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1063">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1064">любое сочетание между 1-200 буквами нижнего или верхнего шкафа, цифрами, символами, специальными символами или пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1064">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1065">строка "SharedAccessKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1065">the string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1066">от нуля до двух символов белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1066">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1067">равный знак (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1067">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1068">от нуля до двух символов белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1068">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1069">любое сочетание из 43 символов, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего шкафа, цифрами, переназначаемой чертой (/) или знаком плюс (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1069">any combination of 43 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1070">равный знак (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1070">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1071">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1071">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1072">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1072">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1073">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1073">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1074">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1074">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1075">Обычное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1075">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1076">Обычное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1076">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Service Bus Connection String-->
<Entity id="b9a6578f-a83f-4fcd-bf44-2130bae49a6f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-storage-account-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1091">Ключ учетной записи azure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1091">Azure storage account key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1092">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1092">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1093">Строка "DefaultEndpointsProtocol" с символами и строками, описанными в рисунке ниже, включая строку "AccountKey".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1093">The string "DefaultEndpointsProtocol" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "AccountKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1094">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1094">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1095">строка "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1095">the string "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1096">от нуля до двух символов белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1096">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1097">равный знак (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1097">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1098">от нуля до двух символов белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1098">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1099">любое сочетание между 1-200 буквами нижнего или верхнего шкафа, цифрами, символами, специальными символами или пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1099">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1100">строка "AccountKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1100">the string "AccountKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1101">от нуля до двух символов белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1101">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1102">равный знак (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1102">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1103">от нуля до двух символов белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1103">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1104">любое сочетание из 86 символов, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего шкафа, цифрами, полосой вперед (/) или знаком плюс (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1104">any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1105">два одинаковых знака (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1105">two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1106">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1106">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1107">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1107">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1108">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1108">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1109">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1109">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1110">Обычное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1110">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1111">Обычное выражение CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter не находит контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1111">The regular expression CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1112">Обычное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1112">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key-->
<Entity id="c7bc98e8-551a-4c35-a92d-d2c8cda714a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="cep_common_example_keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1117">CEP_common_example_keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1117">CEP_common_example_keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1118">(Технически этот тип конфиденциальной информации определяет эти ключевые слова с помощью регулярного выражения, а не списка ключевых слов.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1118">(Technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1119">contoso</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1119">contoso</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1121">northwind</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1121">northwind</span></span>

## <a name="azure-storage-account-key-generic"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1130">служба хранилища Azure учетной записи (общий)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1130">Azure Storage account key (generic)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1131">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1131">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1132">Любое сочетание из 86 букв нижнего или верхнего шкафа, цифр, переднюю черту (/) или знак плюс (+), предшествуют или следуют символы, описанные в рисунке ниже.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1132">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+), preceded or followed by the characters outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1133">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1133">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1134">от нуля до одного из символов (>), апострофа ('), равного знака (=), кавычка (") или знака номеров (#)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1134">zero to one of the greater than symbol (>), apostrophe ('), equal sign (=), quotation mark ("), or number sign (#)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1135">любое сочетание из 86 символов, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего шкафа, цифрами, полосой вперед (/) или знаком плюс (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1135">any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1136">два одинаковых знака (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1136">two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1137">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1137">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1138">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1138">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1139">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1139">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1140">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1140">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1141">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1141">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key (Generic)-->
<Entity id="7ff41bd0-5419-4523-91d6-383b3a37f084" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
## <a name="belgium-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1142">Номер водительских прав в Бельгии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1142">Belgium driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1143">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1143">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1144">10 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1144">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1145">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1145">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1146">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1146">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1147">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1147">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1148">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1148">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1149">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1149">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1150">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1150">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1151">Обычное выражение  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1151">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1152">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1152">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Belgium Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d89fd329-9324-433c-b687-2c37bd5166f3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-national-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1285">Национальный номер Бельгии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1285">Belgium national number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1286">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1286">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1287">11 цифр плюс необязательные делимитеры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1287">11 digits plus optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1288">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1288">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1289">11 цифр, а также разделители:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1289">11 digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1290">шесть цифр и два необязательных периода в формате YY. MM.DD для даты рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1290">six digits and two optional periods in the format YY.MM.DD for date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1291">Необязательный делимитер из точки, тире, пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1291">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1292">три последовательной цифры (нечетные для мужчин, даже для женщин)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1292">three sequential digits (odd for males, even for females)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1293">Необязательный делимитер из точки, тире, пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1293">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1294">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1294">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1295">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1295">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1296">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1296">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1297">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1297">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1298">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1298">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1299">функция Func_belgium_national_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1299">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1300">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_belgium_national_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1300">A keyword from Keyword_belgium_national_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1301">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1301">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1302">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1302">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1303">функция Func_belgium_national_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1303">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1304">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1304">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Belgium National Number -->
       <Entity id="fb969c9e-0fd1-4b18-8091-a2123c5e6a54" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1363">Номер паспорта Бельгии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1363">Belgium passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1364">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1364">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1365">две буквы с шестью цифрами без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1365">two letters followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1366">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1366">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1367">две буквы и шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1367">two letters and followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1368">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1368">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1369">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1369">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1370">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1370">Definition</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1371">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1371">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1372">Обычное выражение  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1372">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1373">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1373">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1374">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date2` находит дату в формате DD MM YY или ключевое слово из `Keywords_eu_passport_date` или `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` найдено</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1374">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date2` finds date in the format DD MM YY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1375">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1375">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1376">Обычное выражение  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1376">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1377">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1377">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d7b1315b-21ca-4774-a32a-596010ff78fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date2" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1378">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1378">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1379">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1379">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

## <a name="belgium-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1404">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость в Бельгии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1404">Belgium value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1405">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1405">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1406">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1406">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1407">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1407">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1408">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1408">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1409">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1409">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1410">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1410">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1411">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1411">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1412">12-символ альфанумерный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1412">12-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1413">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1413">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1414">12-символ альфанумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1414">12-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1415">буквы B или b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1415">a letter B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1416">письмо E или e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1416">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1417">цифру 0</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1417">a digit 0</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1418">цифру от 1 до 9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1418">a digit from 1 to 9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1419">необязательная точка или дефис или пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1419">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1420">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1420">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1421">необязательная точка или дефис или пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1421">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1422">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1422">four digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1423">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1423">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1424">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1424">Yes</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1425">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1425">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1426">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1426">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1427">Функция Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1427">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1428">Ключевое слово Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1428">A keyword from Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1429">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1429">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1430">Функция Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1430">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="85b5b3c3-f2de-4ae8-ac46-fd3cb38bf9ed" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

#### <a name="keyword_belgium_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1432">Keyword_belgium_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1432">Keyword_belgium_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1435">vat no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1435">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1436">numéro t.v.a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1436">numéro t.v.a</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1437">umsatzsteuer-identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1437">umsatzsteuer-identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1438">umsatzsteuernummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1438">umsatzsteuernummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1439">btw</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1439">btw</span></span>

## <a name="brazil-cpf-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1442">Номер CPF в Бразилии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1442">Brazil CPF number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1443">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1443">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1444">11 цифр, которые включают проверочную цифру и могут быть форматированными или неформатированными.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1444">11 digits that include a check digit and can be formatted or unformatted</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1445">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1445">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1446">Форматированный:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1446">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1447">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1447">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1448">период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1448">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1449">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1449">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1450">период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1450">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1451">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1451">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1452">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1452">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1453">две цифры, которые являются контрольными цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1453">two digits that are check digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1454">Unformatted:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1454">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1455">11 цифр, где две последние цифры — проверочные.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1455">11 digits where the last two digits are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1456">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1456">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1457">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1457">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1458">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1458">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1459">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1459">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1460">функция Func_brazil_cpf находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1460">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1461">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_brazil_cpf;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1461">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cpf is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1462">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1462">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1463">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1463">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1464">функция Func_brazil_cpf находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1464">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1465">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1465">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil CPF Number -->
<Entity id="78e09124-f2c3-4656-b32a-c1a132cd2711" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_brazil_cpf"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1467">Keyword_brazil_cpf</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1467">Keyword_brazil_cpf</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1472">Cadastro de Pessoas Físicas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1472">Cadastro de Pessoas Físicas</span></span>

## <a name="brazil-legal-entity-number-cnpj"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1477">Номер юридического лица в Бразилии (CNPJ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1477">Brazil legal entity number (CNPJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1478">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1478">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1479">14 цифр, которые включают регистрационный номер, номер филиала и проверочные цифры, а также разделители.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1479">14 digits that include a registration number, branch number, and check digits, plus delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1480">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1480">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1481">14 цифр, а также разделители:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1481">14 digits, plus delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1482">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1482">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1483">период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1483">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1484">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1484">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1485">период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1485">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1486">три цифры (эти первые восемь цифр являются регистрационным номером)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1486">three digits (these first eight digits are the registration number)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1487">перенарезаемая косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1487">a forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1488">четырехзначный номер филиала</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1488">four-digit branch number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1489">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1489">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1490">две цифры, которые являются контрольными цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1490">two digits that are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1491">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1491">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1492">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1492">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1493">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1493">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1494">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1494">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1495">функция Func_brazil_cnpj находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1495">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1496">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_brazil_cnpj;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1496">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cnpj is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1497">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1497">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1498">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1498">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1499">функция Func_brazil_cnpj находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1499">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1500">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1500">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil Legal Entity Number (CNPJ) -->
<Entity id="9b58b5cd-5e90-4df6-b34f-1ebcc88ceae4" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
