## <a name="brazil-national-identification-card-rg"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1522">Национальная идентификация Бразилии (RG)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1522">Brazil national identification card (RG)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1523">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1523">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1524">Реестр Geral (старый формат): девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1524">Registro Geral (old format): Nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1525">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (новый формат): 11 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1525">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format): 11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1526">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1526">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1527">Registro Geral (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1527">Registro Geral (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1528">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1528">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1529">период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1529">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1530">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1530">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1531">период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1531">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1532">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1532">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1533">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1533">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1534">одна цифра, которая является контрольной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1534">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1535">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1535">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1536">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1536">10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1537">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1537">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1538">одна цифра, которая является контрольной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1538">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1539">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1539">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1540">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1540">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1541">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1541">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1542">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1542">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1543">функция Func_brazil_rg находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1543">The function Func_brazil_rg finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1544">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_brazil_rg;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1544">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_rg is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1545">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1545">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
      <!-- Brazil National ID Card (RG) -->
      <Entity id="486de900-db70-41b3-a886-abdf25af119c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_rg" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_rg" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1546">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1546">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_brazil_rg"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1547">Keyword_brazil_rg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1547">Keyword_brazil_rg</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1548">Cédula de identidade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1548">Cédula de identidade</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1549">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1549">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1550">national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1550">national id</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1551">número de rregistro</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1551">número de rregistro</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1552">registro de Iidentidade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1552">registro de Iidentidade</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1553">registro geral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1553">registro geral</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1554">RG (это ключевое слово является чувствительным к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1554">RG (this keyword is case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1555">RIC (это ключевое слово является чувствительным к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1555">RIC (this keyword is case-sensitive)</span></span> 


## <a name="bulgaria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1556">Номер водительского удостоверения Болгарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1556">Bulgaria driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1557">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1557">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1558">девять цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1558">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1559">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1559">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1560">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1560">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1561">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1561">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1562">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1562">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1563">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1563">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1564">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1564">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1565">Обычное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1565">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1566">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1566">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="66d39258-94c2-43b2-804b-aa312258e54b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>    
```

## <a name="bulgaria-uniform-civil-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1693">Единый гражданский номер Болгарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1693">Bulgaria uniform civil number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1694">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1694">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1695">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1695">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1696">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1696">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1697">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1697">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1698">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1698">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1699">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1699">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1700">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1700">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1701">10 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1701">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1702">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1702">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1703">10 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1703">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1704">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1704">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1705">две цифры, соответствующие порядку рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1705">two digits that correspond to the birth order</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1706">одна цифра, соответствующая полу: четная цифра для мужчин и нечетная цифра для женщин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1706">one digit that corresponds to gender: An even digit for male and an odd digit for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1707">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1707">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1708">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1708">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1709">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1709">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1710">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1710">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1711">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1711">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1712">Функция находит  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1712">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1713">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1713">A keyword from  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1714">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1714">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1715">Функция находит  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1715">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Uniform Civil Number -->
      <Entity id="100d58b1-0a35-4fb1-aa89-e4a86fb53fcc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="bulgaria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1760">Номер паспорта Болгарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1760">Bulgaria passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1761">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1761">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1762">девять цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1762">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1763">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1763">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1764">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1764">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1765">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1765">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1766">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1766">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1767">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1767">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1768">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1768">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1769">Обычное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1769">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1770">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1770">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1771">Обычное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате DD.MM.YYYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1771">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1772">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1772">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1773">Обычное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1773">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1774">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1774">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="f7172b82-c588-4216-845e-4e54e397f29a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1794">Номер банковского счета в Канаде</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1794">Canada bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1795">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1795">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1796">7 или 12 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1796">7 or 12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1797">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1797">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1798">Номер учетной записи Банка Канады — 7 или 12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1798">A Canada Bank Account Number is 7 or 12 digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1799">Транзитный номер банковского счета в Канаде имеет указанный ниже формат.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1799">A Canada bank account transit number is:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1800">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1800">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1801">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1801">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1802">три цифры OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1802">three digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1803">нулевое значение "0"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1803">a zero "0"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1804">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1804">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1805">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1805">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1806">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1806">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1807">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1807">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1808">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1808">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1809">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1809">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1810">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1810">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1811">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1811">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1812">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1812">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1813">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1813">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1814">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1814">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="552e814c-cb50-4d94-bbaa-bb1d1ffb34de" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number" />
   </Pattern>
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1838">Номер водительских прав в Канаде</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1838">Canada driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1839">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1839">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1840">Зависит от провинции.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1840">Varies by province</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1841">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1841">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1842">Различные шаблоны, охватывающие:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1842">Various patterns covering:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1843">Альберта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1843">Alberta</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1844">British Columbia</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1844">British Columbia</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1845">Манитоба</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1845">Manitoba</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1846">New Brunswick</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1846">New Brunswick</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1847">Newfoundland/Labrador</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1847">Newfoundland/Labrador</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1848">Nova Scotia</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1848">Nova Scotia</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1849">Онтарио</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1849">Ontario</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1850">Prince Edward Island</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1850">Prince Edward Island</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1851">Квебек</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1851">Quebec</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1852">Саскачеван</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1852">Saskatchewan</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1853">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1853">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1854">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1854">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1855">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1855">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1856">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1856">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1857">функция Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1857">The function Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1858">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1858">A keyword from Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1859">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1859">A keyword from Keyword_canada_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />

## <a name="canada-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1995">Номер службы здравоохранения Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1995">Canada health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1996">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1996">Format</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1997">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1997">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1998">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1998">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-1999">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-1999">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2000">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2000">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2001">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2001">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2002">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2002">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2003">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2003">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2004">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_health_service_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2004">The regular expression Regex_canada_health_service_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2005">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_health_service_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2005">A keyword from Keyword_canada_health_service_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Health Service Number -->
<Entity id="59c0bf39-7fab-482c-af25-00faa4384c94" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_health_service_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_health_service_number" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2008">personal health number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2008">personal health number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2010">health services</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2010">health services</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2011">speciality services</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2011">speciality services</span></span>

## <a name="canada-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2017">Номер паспорта Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2017">Canada passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2018">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2018">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2019">два верхних буквы с последующим шестью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2019">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2020">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2020">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2021">два верхних буквы с последующим шестью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2021">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2022">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2022">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2023">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2023">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2024">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2024">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2025">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2025">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2026">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2026">The regular expression Regex_canada_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2027">Найдено ключевое слово Keyword_canada_passport_number Keyword_passport или Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2027">A keyword from Keyword_canada_passport_number or Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml 
<!-- Canada Passport Number -->
<Entity id="14d0db8b-498a-43ed-9fca-f6097ae687eb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2028">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2028">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_canada_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2029">Keyword_canada_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2029">Keyword_canada_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2030">canadian citizenship</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2030">canadian citizenship</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2031">canadian passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2031">canadian passport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2032">passport application</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2032">passport application</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2033">passport photos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2033">passport photos</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2034">certified translator</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2034">certified translator</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2035">canadian citizens</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2035">canadian citizens</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2036">processing times</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2036">processing times</span></span>

## <a name="canada-personal-health-identification-number-phin"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2057">Идентификационный номер личного здоровья Канады (PHIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2057">Canada personal health identification number (PHIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2058">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2058">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2059">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2059">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2060">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2060">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2061">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2061">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2062">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2062">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2063">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2063">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2064">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2064">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2065">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2065">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2066">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_phin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2066">The regular expression Regex_canada_phin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2067">Найдены по крайней мере два Keyword_canada_phin или Keyword_canada_provinces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2067">At least two keywords from Keyword_canada_phin or Keyword_canada_provinces are found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada PHIN -->
<Entity id="722e12ac-c89a-4ec8-a1b7-fea3469f89db" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_phin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_phin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_provinces" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-social-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2100">Номер социального страхования Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2100">Canada social insurance number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2101">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2101">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2102">девять цифр с необязательными дефисами или пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2102">nine digits with optional hyphens or spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2103">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2103">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2104">Форматированный:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2104">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2105">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2105">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2106">дефис или пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2106">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2107">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2107">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2108">дефис или пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2108">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2109">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2109">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2110">Unformatted: nine digits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2110">Unformatted: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2111">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2111">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2112">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2112">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2113">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2113">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2114">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2114">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2115">Функция Func_canadian_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2115">The function Func_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2116">По крайней мере два из следующих шаблонов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2116">At least two of the following patterns:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2117">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2117">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2118">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin_collaborative;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2118">A keyword from Keyword_sin_collaborative is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2119">функция Func_eu_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2119">The function Func_eu_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2120">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2120">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2121">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2121">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2122">функция Func_unformatted_canadian_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2122">The function Func_unformatted_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2123">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2123">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2124">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2124">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="a2f29c85-ecb8-4514-a610-364790c0773e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_canadian_sin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Func_eu_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_canadian_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="chile-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2149">Номер удостоверения личности в Чили</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2149">Chile identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2150">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2150">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2151">семь-восемь цифр плюс делимитеры контрольная цифра или буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2151">seven to eight digits plus delimiters a check digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2152">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2152">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2153">семь-восемь цифр плюс делимитеры:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2153">seven to eight digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2154">от одной до двух цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2154">one to two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2155">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2155">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2156">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2156">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2157">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2157">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2158">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2158">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2159">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2159">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2160">одна цифра или буква (не чувствительная к делу), которая является проверяемой цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2160">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2161">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2161">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2162">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2162">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2163">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2163">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2164">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2164">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2165">функция Func_chile_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2165">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2166">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_chile_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2166">A keyword from Keyword_chile_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2167">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2167">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2168">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2168">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2169">функция Func_chile_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2169">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2170">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2170">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Chile Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="4e979794-49a0-407e-a0b9-2c536937b925" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="china-resident-identity-card-prc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2207">Номер удостоверения резидента Китая (PRC)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2207">China resident identity card (PRC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2208">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2208">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2209">18 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2209">18 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2210">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2210">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2211">18 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2211">18 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2212">шесть цифр, которые являются адресным кодом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2212">six digits that are an address code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2213">восемь цифр в форме YYYYYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2213">eight digits in the form YYYYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2214">три цифры, которые являются кодом заказа</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2214">three digits that are an order code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2215">одна цифра, которая является контрольной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2215">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2216">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2216">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2217">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2217">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2218">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2218">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2219">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2219">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2220">функция Func_china_resident_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2220">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2221">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_china_resident_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2221">A keyword from Keyword_china_resident_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2222">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2222">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2223">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2223">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2224">функция Func_china_resident_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2224">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2225">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2225">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- China Resident Identity Card (PRC) Number -->
<Entity id="c92daa86-2d16-4871-901f-816b3f554fc1" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2226">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2226">Keywords</span></span>

### <a name="keyword_china_resident_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2227">Keyword_china_resident_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2227">Keyword_china_resident_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2228">Resident Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2228">Resident Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2229">PRC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2229">PRC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2230">National Identification Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2230">National Identification Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2231">身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2231">身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2232">居民 身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2232">居民 身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2233">居民身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2233">居民身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2234">鉴定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2234">鉴定</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2235">身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2235">身分證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2236">居民 身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2236">居民 身份證</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2237">鑑定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2237">鑑定</span></span> 

   
## <a name="credit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2238">Номер кредитной карты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2238">Credit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2239">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2239">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2240">От 14 до 16 цифр, которые могут быть отформатированы или неформатированы (dddd), и которые должны пройти тест Luhn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2240">14 to 16 digits that can be formatted or unformatted (dddddddddddddddd) and that must pass the Luhn test.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2241">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2241">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2242">Обнаруживает карты всех крупных брендов по всему миру, включая карты Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, подарочные карты и карточки для посетителей.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2242">Detects cards from all major brands worldwide, including Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, gift cards, and diner cards.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2243">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2243">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2244">Да (рассчитывается по алгоритму Луна).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2244">Yes, the Luhn checksum</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2245">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2245">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2246">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2246">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2247">Функция Func_credit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2247">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2248">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2248">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2249">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_cc_verification;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2249">A keyword from Keyword_cc_verification is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2250">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_cc_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2250">A keyword from Keyword_cc_name is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2251">функция Func_expiration_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2251">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2252">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2252">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2253">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2253">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2254">функция Func_credit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2254">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2255">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2255">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Credit Card Number -->
<Entity id="50842eb7-edc8-4019-85dd-5a5c1f2bb085" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_verification" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_name" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2515">Номер водительских прав в Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2515">Croatia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2516">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2516">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2517">восемь цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2517">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2518">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2518">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2519">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2519">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2520">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2520">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2521">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2521">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2522">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2522">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2523">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2523">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2524">Обычное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2524">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2525">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2525">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="005b3ef1-47dd-4e68-bb02-c6db484d00f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2649">Номер удостоверения личности в Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2649">Croatia identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2650">Эта сущность включена в тип конфиденциальной информации о номере национального идентификации ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2650">This entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2651">Он доступен в виде отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2651">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2652">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2652">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2653">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2653">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2654">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2654">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2655">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2655">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2656">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2656">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2657">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2657">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2658">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2658">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2659">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2659">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2660">функция Func_croatia_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2660">The function Func_croatia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2661">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_croatia_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2661">A keyword from Keyword_croatia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Croatia Identity Card Number-->
<Entity id="ff12f884-c20a-4189-b185-34c8e7258d47" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_croatia_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2692">Номер паспорта Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2692">Croatia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2693">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2693">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2694">девять цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2694">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2695">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2695">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2696">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2696">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2697">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2697">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2698">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2698">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2699">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2699">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2700">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2700">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2701">Обычное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2701">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2702">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2702">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2703">Обычное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате DD.MM.YYYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2703">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2704">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2704">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2705">Обычное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2705">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2706">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2706">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Croatia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7d7a729d-32d8-4204-8d01-d5e6a6c25581" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2707">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2707">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2719">Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2719">Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

## <a name="croatia-personal-identification-oib-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2724">Личный идентификационный номер (OIB) в Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2724">Croatia personal identification (OIB) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2725">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2725">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2726">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2726">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2727">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2727">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2728">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2728">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2729">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2729">10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2730">окончательная цифра — это контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2730">final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2731">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2731">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2732">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2732">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2733">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2733">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2734">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2734">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2735">функция Func_croatia_oib_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2735">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2736">Ключевое слово из Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2736">A keyword from Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2737">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2737">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2738">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2738">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2739">функция Func_croatia_oib_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2739">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2740">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2740">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Personal Identification (OIB) Number -->
      <Entity id="31983b6d-db95-4eb2-a630-b44bd091968d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2771">Номер лицензии для водителей Кипра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2771">Cyprus drivers license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2772">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2772">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2773">12 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2773">12 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2774">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2774">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2775">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2775">12 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2776">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2776">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2777">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2777">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2778">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2778">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2779">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2779">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2780">Обычное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2780">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2781">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2781">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="356fa104-f9ac-4aff-a0e4-2e6e65ea06c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2906">Удостоверение личности на Кипре</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2906">Cyprus identity card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2907">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2907">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2908">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2908">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2909">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2909">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2910">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2910">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2911">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2911">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2912">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2912">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2913">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2913">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2914">10 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2914">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2915">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2915">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2916">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2916">10 digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2917">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2917">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2918">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2918">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2919">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2919">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2920">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2920">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2921">Обычное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2921">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2922">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2922">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml 
      <!-- Cyprus Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="3ba8afe5-7a6c-4929-8247-0001b6878438" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2923">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2923">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2924">Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2924">Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card</span></span>
