- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2928">national identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2928">national identification number</span></span>

## <a name="cyprus-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2931">Номер паспорта Кипра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2931">Cyprus passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2932">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2932">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2933">одна буква с 6-8 цифрами без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2933">one letter followed by 6-8 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2934">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2934">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2935">одна буква с шестью или восемью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2935">one letter followed by six to eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2936">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2936">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2937">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2937">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2938">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2938">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2939">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2939">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2940">Обычное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2940">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2941">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2941">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2942">Регулярное выражение `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date` находит дату в формате DD/MM/YYYY или найдено ключевое слово `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2942">The regular expression `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD/MM/YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2943">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2943">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2944">Обычное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2944">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2945">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2945">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>  
    
```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="9193e2e8-7f8c-43c1-a274-ac40d651936f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2958">Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2958">Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number</span></span>

## <a name="cyprus-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2974">Идентификационный номер налога на Кипр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2974">Cyprus tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2975">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2975">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2976">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2976">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2977">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2977">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2978">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2978">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2979">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2979">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2980">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2980">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2981">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2981">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2982">восемь цифр и одна буква в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2982">eight digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2983">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2983">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2984">восемь цифр и одна буква:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2984">eight digits and one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2985">"0" или "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2985">a "0" or "9"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2986">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2986">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2987">одна буква (не деликатная)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2987">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2988">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2988">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2989">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2989">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2990">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2990">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2991">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2991">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2992">Функция находит  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2992">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2993">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2993">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2994">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2994">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-2995">Функция находит  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-2995">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="40e64bd9-55f3-4a09-9bd6-1db18dced9dd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="czech-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3023">Номер чешского водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3023">Czech driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3024">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3024">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3025">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3025">two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3026">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3026">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3027">восемь букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3027">eight letters and digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3028">буква "E" (не в случае)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3028">letter 'E' (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3029">письмо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3029">a letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3030">пробел (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3030">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3031">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3031">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3032">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3032">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3033">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3033">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3034">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3034">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3035">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3035">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3036">Обычное выражение  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3036">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3037">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3037">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <Entity id="86b40d3b-d8ea-4c36-aab0-ef9416a6769c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="czech-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3163">Номер чешского паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3163">Czech passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3164">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3164">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3165">восемь цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3165">eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3166">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3166">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3167">восемь цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3167">eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3168">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3168">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3169">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3169">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3170">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3170">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3171">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3171">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3172">Обычное выражение  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3172">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3173">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3173">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3174">Обычное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате DD.MM.YYYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3174">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3175">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3175">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3176">Обычное выражение  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3176">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3177">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3177">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Czech Republic Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7bcd8ce8-5e92-4bbe-bc92-fa669f0369fa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3178">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3178">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number_common"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3179">Keywords_eu_passport_number_common</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3179">Keywords_eu_passport_number_common</span></span>

## <a name="czech-personal-identity-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3199">Чешский персональный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3199">Czech personal identity number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3200">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3200">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3201">девять цифр с необязательным переназначаемой чертой (старый формат) 10 цифр с необязательным переназначе-ным слэшем (новый формат)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3201">nine digits with optional forward slash (old format) 10 digits with optional forward slash (new format)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3202">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3202">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3203">девять цифр (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3203">nine digits (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3204">шесть цифр, которые представляют дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3204">six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3205">необязательный слэш</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3205">an optional forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3206">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3206">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3207">10 цифр (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3207">10 digits (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3208">шесть цифр, которые представляют дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3208">six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3209">необязательный слэш</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3209">an optional forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3210">четыре цифры, где последняя цифра — это контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3210">four digits where last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3211">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3211">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3212">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3212">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3213">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3213">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3214">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3214">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3215">функция Func_czech_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3215">The function Func_czech_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3216">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_czech_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3216">A keyword from Keyword_czech_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3217">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3217">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3218">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3218">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3219">Функция Func_czech_id_card_new_format контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3219">The function Func_czech_id_card_new_format finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3220">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3220">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
      <!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
      <Entity id="60c0725a-4eb6-455b-9dda-05d8a7396497" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_czech_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3000.000">
          <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
            <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card_new_format" />
          </Pattern>
        </Version>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3267">Номер водительских прав Дании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3267">Denmark driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3268">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3268">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3269">восемь цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3269">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3270">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3270">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3271">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3271">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3272">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3272">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3273">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3273">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3274">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3274">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3275">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3275">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3276">Обычное выражение  `Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3276">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3277">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3277">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Denmark Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="98a95812-6203-451a-a220-d39870ebef0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3286">lic драйвера</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3286">driver lic</span></span>

## <a name="denmark-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3401">Номер паспорта Дании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3401">Denmark passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3402">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3402">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3403">девять цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3403">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3404">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3404">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3405">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3405">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3406">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3406">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3407">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3407">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3408">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3408">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3409">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3409">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3410">Обычное выражение  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3410">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3411">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3411">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3412">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date2` находит дату в формате DD MM YY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из найдено</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3412">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date2` finds date in the format DD MM YY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3413">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3413">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3414">Обычное выражение  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3414">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3415">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3415">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Denmark Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="25e8c47e-e6fe-4884-a211-74898f8c0196" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date2" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="denmark-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3435">Личный идентификационный номер Дании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3435">Denmark personal identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3436">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3436">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3437">10 цифр, содержащих дефис.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3437">10 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3438">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3438">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3439">10 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3439">10 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3440">шесть цифр в формате DDMMYY, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3440">six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3441">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3441">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3442">четыре цифры, в которых окончательная цифра — это контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3442">four digits where the final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3443">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3443">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3444">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3444">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3445">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3445">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3446">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3446">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3447">Регулярное выражение Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3447">The regular expression Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3448">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_denmark_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3448">A keyword from Keyword_denmark_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3449">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3449">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3450">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3450">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3451">Регулярное выражение Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3451">The regular expression Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3452">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3452">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
      <!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="6c4f2fef-56e1-4c00-8093-88d7a01cf460" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_denmark_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="drug-enforcement-agency-dea-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3524">Номер Агентства по принудиванию к наркотикам (DEA)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3524">Drug Enforcement Agency (DEA) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3525">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3525">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3526">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3526">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3527">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3527">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3528">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3528">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3529">одна буква (не деликатная) из этого набора возможных букв: abcdefghjklmnprstux, который является кодом регистратора</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3529">one letter (not case-sensitive) from this set of possible letters: abcdefghjklmnprstux, which is a registrant code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3530">одна буква (не деликатная), которая является первой буквой фамилии или цифры "9" регистратора.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3530">one letter (not case-sensitive), which is the first letter of the registrant's last name or digit '9'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3531">семь цифр, последним из которых является контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3531">seven digits, the last of which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3532">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3532">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3533">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3533">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3534">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3534">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3535">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3535">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3536">функция Func_dea_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3536">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3537">Найдено `Keyword_dea_number` ключевое слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3537">A keyword from `Keyword_dea_number` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3538">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3538">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3539">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3539">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3540">функция Func_dea_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3540">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3541">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3541">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- DEA Number -->
    <Entity id="9a5445ad-406e-43eb-8bd7-cac17ab6d0e4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
      </Pattern>
      <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.1207.000" maxEngineVersion="15.20.3134.000">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Version>
      <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3135.000">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_dea_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Version>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3542">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3542">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_dea_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3543">Keyword_dea_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3543">Keyword_dea_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3544">dea</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3544">dea</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3545">dea #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3545">dea#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3546">администрирование по принудительных лекарственных препарат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3546">drug enforcement administration</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3547">агентство по принудиванию к наркотикам</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3547">drug enforcement agency</span></span>


## <a name="estonia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3548">Номер водительских прав Эстонии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3548">Estonia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3549">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3549">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3550">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3550">two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3551">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3551">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3552">две буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3552">two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3553">буквы "ET" (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3553">the letters "ET" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3554">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3554">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3555">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3555">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3556">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3556">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3557">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3557">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3558">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3558">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3559">Обычное выражение  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3559">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3560">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3560">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="51da8171-da70-4cc1-9d65-055a59ca4f83" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="estonia-personal-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3686">Код личной идентификации Эстонии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3686">Estonia Personal Identification Code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3687">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3687">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3688">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3688">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3689">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3689">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3690">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3690">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3691">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3691">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3692">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3692">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3693">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3693">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3694">11 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3694">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3695">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3695">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3696">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3696">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3697">одна цифра, соответствующая полу и столетию рождения (нечетное число мужчин, даже женское; 1-2: 19-й век; 3-4: 20-й век; 5-6: 21 век)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3697">one digit that corresponds to sex and century of birth (odd number male, even number female; 1-2: 19th century; 3-4: 20th century; 5-6: 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3698">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3698">six digits that correspond to date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3699">три цифры, соответствующие последовательному номеру, разделяющей лиц, родившихся в ту же дату</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3699">three digits that correspond to a serial number separating persons born on the same date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3700">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3700">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3701">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3701">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3702">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3702">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3703">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3703">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3704">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3704">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3705">Функция находит  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3705">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3706">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3706">A keyword from  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3707">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3707">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3708">Функция находит  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3708">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Personal Identification Code -->
      <Entity id="bfb26de6-dad5-4d48-ab72-4789cdd0654c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="estonia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3741">Номер паспорта Эстонии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3741">Estonia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3742">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3742">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3743">одна буква с семью цифрами без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3743">one letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3744">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3744">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3745">одна буква, за которой следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3745">one letter followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3746">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3746">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3747">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3747">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3748">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3748">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3749">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3749">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3750">Обычное выражение  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3750">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3751">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3751">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3752">Обычное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате DD.MM.YYYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3752">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3753">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3753">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3754">Обычное выражение  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3754">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3755">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3755">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="61f7073a-509e-425b-a754-bc01bb5d5b8c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="eu-debit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3773">Номер дебетовой карты, выпущенной в ЕС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3773">EU debit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3774">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3774">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3775">16 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3775">16 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3776">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3776">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3777">Сложный и надежный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3777">Complex and robust pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3778">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3778">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3779">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3779">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3780">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3780">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3781">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3781">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3782">Функция Func_eu_debit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3782">The function Func_eu_debit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3783">Верно по меньшей мере одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3783">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3784">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_eu_debit_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3784">A keyword from Keyword_eu_debit_card is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3785">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_card_terms_dict;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3785">A keyword from Keyword_card_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3786">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_card_security_terms_dict;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3786">A keyword from Keyword_card_security_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3787">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3787">A keyword from Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3788">функция Func_expiration_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3788">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-3789">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-3789">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- EU Debit Card Number -->
    <Entity id="0e9b3178-9678-47dd-a509-37222ca96b42" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_eu_debit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_eu_debit_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_security_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- [<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4235">U.K.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4235">U.K.</span></span>](#uk-unique-taxpayer-reference-number)


## <a name="finland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4236">Номер водительского удостоверения Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4236">Finland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4237">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4237">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4238">10 цифр, содержащих дефис.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4238">10 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4239">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4239">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4240">10 цифр, содержащих дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4240">10 digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4241">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4241">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4242">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4242">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4243">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4243">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4244">цифру или букву</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4244">a digit or letter</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4245">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4245">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4246">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4246">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4247">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4247">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4248">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4248">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4249">Обычное выражение  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4249">The regular expression  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4250">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4250">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Finland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="bb3b27a3-79bd-4ac4-81a7-f9fca3c7d1a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-european-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4381">Номер европейского медицинского страхования Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4381">Finland european health insurance number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4382">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4382">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4383">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4383">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4384">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4384">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4385">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4385">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4386">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4386">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4387">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4387">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4388">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4388">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4389">20-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4389">20-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4390">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4390">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4391">20-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4391">20-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4392">10 цифр - 8024680246</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4392">10 digits - 8024680246</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4393">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4393">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4394">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4394">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4395">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4395">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4396">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4396">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4397">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4397">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4398">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4398">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4399">В regex Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4399">The regex Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4400">Найдено ключевое слово Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4400">A keyword from Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finland European Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="60f75aed-81bf-4625-89b0-0846b9248ee7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4418">Национальный ID Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4418">Finland national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4419">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4419">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4420">шесть цифр плюс символ, указывающий на столетие плюс три цифры плюс контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4420">six digits plus a character indicating a century plus three digits plus a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4421">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4421">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4422">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4422">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4423">шесть цифр в формате DDMMYY, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4423">six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are a date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4424">маркер века (или '-', '+' или 'a')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4424">century marker (either '-', '+' or 'a')</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4425">трехзначный личный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4425">three-digit personal identification number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4426">цифру или букву (случай нечувствительный), которая является контрольной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4426">a digit or letter (case insensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4427">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4427">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4428">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4428">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4429">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4429">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4430">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4430">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4431">функция Func_finnish_national_id контента, который соответствует шаблону</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4431">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4432">найдено ключевое слово Keyword_finnish_national_id из Keyword_finnish_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4432">a keyword from Keyword_finnish_national_id is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4433">проходит проверку</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4433">the checksum passes</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4434">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4434">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4435">функция Func_finnish_national_id контента, который соответствует шаблону</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4435">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4436">проходит проверку</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4436">the checksum passes</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finnish National ID-->
      <Entity id="338FD995-4CB5-4F87-AD35-79BD1DD926C1" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4485">Номер паспорта Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4485">Finland passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4486">Эта сущность доступна в типе конфиденциальной информации по номеру паспорта ЕС и доступна в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4486">This entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4487">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4487">Format</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4488">сочетание девяти букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4488">combination of nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4489">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4489">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4490">сочетание девяти букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4490">combination of nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4491">две буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4491">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4492">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4492">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4493">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4493">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4494">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4494">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4495">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4495">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4496">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4496">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4497">Обычное выражение `Regex_finland_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4497">The regular expression `Regex_finland_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4498">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keyword_finland_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4498">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_finland_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4499">Обычное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате DD.MM.YYYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4499">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4500">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4500">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4501">Обычное выражение `Regex_finland_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4501">The regular expression `Regex_finland_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4502">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keyword_finland_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4502">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_finland_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d1685ac3-1d3a-40f8-8198-32ef5669c7a5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_finland_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_finland_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4503">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4503">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="france-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4526">Номер водительских прав Во Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4526">France driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4527">Эта сущность доступна в типе конфиденциальной информации о номере лицензии водителя ЕС и доступна в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4527">This entity is available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4528">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4528">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4529">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4529">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4530">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4530">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4531">12 цифр с проверкой подлинности, чтобы избежать путаницы с похожими шаблонами, например французскими номерами телефонов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4531">12 digits with validation to discount similar patterns such as French telephone numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4532">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4532">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4533">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4533">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4534">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4534">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4535">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4535">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4536">функция Func_french_drivers_license контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4536">the function Func_french_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4537">ключевое слово Keyword_french_drivers_license найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4537">a keyword from Keyword_french_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="18e55a36-a01b-4b0f-943d-dc10282a1824" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_french_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```
