## <a name="france-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4664">Номер медицинского страхования Во Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4664">France health insurance number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4665">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4665">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4666">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4666">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4667">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4667">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4668">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4668">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4669">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4669">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4670">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4670">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4671">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4671">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4672">21-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4672">21-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4673">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4673">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4674">21-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4674">21-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4675">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4675">10 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4676">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4676">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4677">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4677">10 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4678">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4678">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4679">цифру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4679">a digit</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4680">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4680">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4681">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4681">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4682">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4682">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4683">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4683">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4684">regex Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4684">the regex Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4685">найдено ключевое слово Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4685">a keyword from Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="9bc2069e-76df-4ff9-ac02-2f519469e236" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4686">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4686">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_france_health_insurance_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4687">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4687">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4688">карта страхования</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4688">insurance card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4689">carte vitale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4689">carte vitale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4690">carte d'assuré social</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4690">carte d'assuré social</span></span>


## <a name="france-national-id-card-cni"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4691">Национальная id-карта Франции (CNI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4691">France national id card (CNI)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4692">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4692">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4693">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4693">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4694">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4694">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4695">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4695">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4696">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4696">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4697">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4697">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4698">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4698">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4699">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4699">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4700">регулярное выражение Regex_france_cni находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4700">The regular expression Regex_france_cni finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4701">Ключевое слово Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4701">A keyword from Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France CNI -->
    <Entity id="f741ac74-1bc0-4665-b69b-f0c7f927c0c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="65">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_france_cni" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_france_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4703">Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4703">Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4706">carte nationale d'idenite no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4706">carte nationale d'idenite no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4707">cni #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4707">cni#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4714">numéro de carte vitale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4714">numéro de carte vitale</span></span>

   
## <a name="france-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4715">Номер паспорта Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4715">France passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4716">Эта сущность доступна в типе конфиденциальной информации по номеру паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4716">This entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4717">Он также доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4717">It's also available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4718">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4718">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4719">девять цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4719">nine digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4720">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4720">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4721">девять цифр и букв:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4721">nine digits and letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4722">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4722">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4723">две буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4723">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4724">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4724">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4725">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4725">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4726">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4726">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4727">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4727">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4728">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4728">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4729">Функция находит `Func_fr_passport` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4729">The function `Func_fr_passport` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4730">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4730">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4731">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date3` находит дату в формате DD MM YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4731">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4732">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4732">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4733">Функция находит `Func_fr_passport` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4733">The function `Func_fr_passport` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4734">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4734">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- France Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="3008b884-8c8c-4cd8-a289-99f34fc7ff5d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4753">passeportnon</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4753">passeportnon</span></span>

## <a name="france-social-security-number-insee"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4765">Номер социального обеспечения Франции (INSEE)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4765">France social security number (INSEE)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4766">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4766">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4767">15 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4767">15 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4768">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4768">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4769">Должен соответствовать одному из двух шаблонов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4769">Must match one of two patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4770">13 цифр с последующим пространством с двумя цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4770">13 digits followed by a space followed by two digits</span></span><br/>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4771">или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4771">or</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4772">15 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4772">15 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4773">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4773">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4774">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4774">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4775">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4775">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4776">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4776">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4777">Функция находит `Func_french_insee` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4777">The function `Func_french_insee` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4778">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_fr_insee;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4778">A keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4779">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4779">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4780">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4780">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4781">Функция Func_french_insee или Func_fr_insee находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4781">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4782">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4782">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France INSEE -->
    <Entity id="71f62b97-efe0-4aa1-aa49-e14de253619d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4783">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4783">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_fr_insee"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4784">Keyword_fr_insee</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4784">Keyword_fr_insee</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4785">code sécu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4785">code sécu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4786">d'identité nationale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4786">d'identité nationale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4787">insee</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4787">insee</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4788">fssn #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4788">fssn#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4789">le numéro d'identification nationale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4789">le numéro d'identification nationale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4790">le code de la sécurité sociale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4790">le code de la sécurité sociale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4791">national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4791">national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4792">national identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4792">national identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4793">no d'identité</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4793">no d'identité</span></span>

no. d'identité</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-p133">no. d'identité</span></span>

no. d'identite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-p134">no. d'identite</span></span>

## <a name="france-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4813">Номер идентификации налога во Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4813">France tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4814">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4814">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4815">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4815">13 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4816">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4816">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4817">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4817">13 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4818">Одна цифра, которая должна быть 0, 1, 2 или 3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4818">One digit that must be 0, 1, 2, or 3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4819">Одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4819">One digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4820">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4820">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4821">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4821">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4822">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4822">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4823">три цифры; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4823">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4824">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4824">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4825">три цифры; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4825">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4826">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4826">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4827">Три контрольных цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4827">Three check digits</span></span> 

  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4828">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4828">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4829">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4829">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4830">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4830">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4831">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4831">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4832">Функция находит  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4832">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4833">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4833">A keyword from  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4834">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4834">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4835">Функция находит  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4835">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- France Tax Identification Number (numéro SPI.) -->
      <Entity id="ed59e77e-171d-442c-9ec1-88e2ebcb5b0a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4836">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4836">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4837">Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4837">Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4838">numéro d'identification fiscale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4838">numéro d'identification fiscale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4839">tax id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4839">tax id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4840">идентификация налога нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4840">tax identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4841">идентификационный номер налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4841">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4842">нет налога #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4842">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4843">нет налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4843">tax no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4844">налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4844">tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4845">номер регистрации налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4845">tax registration number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4846">таксомоторный #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4846">taxid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4847">taxidno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4847">taxidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4848">taxidnumber #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4848">taxidnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4849">taxno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4849">taxno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4850">taxnumber #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4850">taxnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4851">taxnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4851">taxnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4852">tin id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4852">tin id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4853">олово нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4853">tin no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4854">олово #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4854">tin#</span></span>


## <a name="france-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4855">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость во Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4855">France value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4856">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4856">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4857">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4857">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4858">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4858">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4859">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4859">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4860">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4860">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4861">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4861">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4862">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4862">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4863">13 символов альфанумерного шаблона</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4863">13 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4864">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4864">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4865">13 символов альфанумерного шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4865">13 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4866">две буквы - FR (случай нечувствительный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4866">two letters  - FR (case insensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4867">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4867">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4868">две буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4868">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4869">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4869">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4870">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4870">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4871">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4871">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4872">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4872">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4873">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4873">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4874">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4874">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4875">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4875">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4876">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4876">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4877">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4877">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4878">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4878">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4879">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4879">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4880">Найдено ключевое слово Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4880">A keyword from Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4881">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4881">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4882">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4882">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="949121e6-ad9f-4379-8731-710342baea78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4883">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4883">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_france_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4884">Keyword_France_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4884">Keyword_France_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4885">номер НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4885">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4886">vat no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4886">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4887">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4887">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4888">налог на добавленную стоимость</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4888">value added tax</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4889">идентификация сирены без numéro d'identification taxe sur valeur ajoutée</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4889">siren identification no numéro d'identification taxe sur valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4890">taxe valeur ajoutée</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4890">taxe valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4891">taxe sur la valeur ajoutée</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4891">taxe sur la valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4892">n° tva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4892">n° tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4893">numéro de tva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4893">numéro de tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4894">сирена numéro d'identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4894">numéro d'identification siren</span></span>


## <a name="germany-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4895">Номер водительских прав в Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4895">Germany driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4896">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации входит в тип конфиденциальной информации номер лицензии водителя ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4896">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4897">Он также доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4897">It's also available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4898">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4898">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4899">сочетание 11 цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4899">combination of 11 digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4900">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4900">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4901">11 цифр и букв (не чувствительных к делу):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4901">11 digits and letters (not case-sensitive):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4902">цифру или букву</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4902">a digit or letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4903">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4903">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4904">шесть цифр или букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4904">six digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4905">цифру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4905">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4906">цифру или букву</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4906">a digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4907">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4907">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4908">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4908">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4909">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4909">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4910">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4910">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4911">Функция Func_german_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4911">The function Func_german_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4912">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_german_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4912">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-4913">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-4913">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="91da9335-1edb-45b7-a95f-5fe41a16c63c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_german_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5062">Номер удостоверения личности в Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5062">Germany identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5063">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5063">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5064">с 1 ноября 2010 г.: девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5064">since 1 November 2010: Nine letters and digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5065">с 1 апреля 1987 г. по 31 октября 2010 г.: 10 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5065">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010: 10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5066">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5066">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5067">с 1 ноября 2010 г.:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5067">since 1 November 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5068">одна буква (не деликатная)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5068">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5069">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5069">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5070">с 1 апреля 1987 г. по 31 октября 2010 г.:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5070">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5071">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5071">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5072">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5072">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5073">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5073">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5074">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5074">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5075">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5075">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5076">регулярное выражение Regex_germany_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5076">The regular expression Regex_germany_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5077">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_germany_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5077">A keyword from Keyword_germany_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="e577372f-c42e-47a0-9d85-bebed1c237d4" recommendedConfidence="65" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_germany_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_germany_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5078">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5078">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_germany_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5079">Keyword_germany_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5079">Keyword_germany_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5080">ausweis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5080">ausweis</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5081">gpid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5081">gpid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5082">идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5082">identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5083">identifikation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5083">identifikation</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5084">identifizierungsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5084">identifizierungsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5085">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5085">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5086">номер удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5086">identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5087">id-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5087">id-nummer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5089">personalausweis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5089">personalausweis</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5091">persönliche identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5091">persönliche identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5092">persönliche-id-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5092">persönliche-id-nummer</span></span>


## <a name="germany-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5093">Номер паспорта Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5093">Germany passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5094">Эта сущность включена в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступна в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5094">This entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5095">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5095">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5096">10 цифр или букв.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5096">10 digits or letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5097">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5097">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5098">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5098">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5099">первый символ — это цифры или буквы из этого набора (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5099">first character is a digit or a letter from this set (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5100">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5100">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5101">пять цифр или букв из этого набора (C, H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5101">five digits or letters from this set (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5102">цифру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5102">a digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5103">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5103">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5104">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5104">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5105">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5105">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5106">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5106">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5107">функция Func_german_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5107">The function Func_german_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5108">Ключевое слово `Keyword_german_passport` из `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5108">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` or `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5109">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5109">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5110">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5110">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5111">функция Func_german_passport_data находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5111">The function Func_german_passport_data finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5112">Ключевое слово `Keyword_german_passport` из `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5112">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` or `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5113">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5113">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="2e3da144-d42b-47ed-b123-fbf78604e52c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport_data" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5132">passportnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5132">passportnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5133">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5133">passport number</span></span>

## <a name="germany-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5136">Идентификационный номер налога в Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5136">Germany tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5137">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5137">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5138">11 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5138">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5139">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5139">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5140">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5140">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5141">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5141">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5142">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5142">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5143">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5143">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5144">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5144">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5145">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5145">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5146">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5146">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5147">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5147">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5148">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5148">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5149">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5149">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5150">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5150">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5151">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5151">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5152">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5152">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5153">Функция находит  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5153">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5154">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5154">A keyword from  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5155">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5155">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5156">Функция находит  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5156">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Germany Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="43316a89-9880-40cf-b980-04bc7eefcec5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5157">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5157">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5164">идентификация налога нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5164">tax identification no</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5166">нет налога #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5166">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5167">нет налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5167">tax no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5168">налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5168">tax number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5170">таксомоторный #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5170">taxid#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5173">taxno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5173">taxno#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5176">tin id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5176">tin id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5177">олово нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5177">tin no</span></span>

## <a name="germany-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5182">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость в Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5182">Germany value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5183">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5183">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5184">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5184">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5185">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5185">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5186">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5186">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5187">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5187">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5188">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5188">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5189">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5189">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5190">Альфанумерный шаблон 11 символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5190">11 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5191">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5191">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5192">11-символ альфанумерного шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5192">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5193">буква D или d</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5193">a letter D or d</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5194">письмо E или e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5194">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5195">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5195">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5196">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5196">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5197">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5197">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5198">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5198">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5199">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5199">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5200">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5200">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5201">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5201">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5202">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5202">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5203">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5203">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5204">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5204">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5205">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5205">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5206">Ключевое слово Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5206">A keyword from Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5207">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5207">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5208">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5208">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Germany Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="db177eb2-8811-4842-bffc-128c14aa219f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5209">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5209">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5210">Keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5210">Keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5211">номер НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5211">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5212">vat no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5212">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5213">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5213">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5214">vat# mehrwertsteuer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5214">vat#  mehrwertsteuer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5215">mwst</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5215">mwst</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5216">mehrwertsteuer identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5216">mehrwertsteuer identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5217">nummer mehrwertsteuer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5217">mehrwertsteuer nummer</span></span>


## <a name="greece-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5218">Номер водительских прав Греции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5218">Greece driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5219">Эта сущность включена в тип конфиденциальной информации о номере лицензии в ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5219">This entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5220">Он также доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5220">It is also available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5221">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5221">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5222">девять цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5222">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5223">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5223">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5224">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5224">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5225">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5225">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5226">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5226">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5227">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5227">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5228">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5228">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5229">Обычное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5229">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5230">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5230">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="7a2200b5-aacf-4e3c-ab36-136d3e68b7da" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
