### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5357">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5357">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5358">Сочетание 7–8 букв и чисел, а также тире.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5358">Combination of 7-8 letters and numbers plus a dash</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5359">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5359">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5360">Семь букв и чисел (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5360">Seven letters and numbers (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5361">одна буква (любая буква греческого алфавита);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5361">One letter (any letter of the Greek alphabet)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5362">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5362">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5363">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5363">Six digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5364">Восемь букв и чисел (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5364">Eight letters and numbers (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5365">две буквы, которые в прописном виде есть как в греческом, так и латинском алфавите (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5365">Two letters whose uppercase character occurs in both the Greek and Latin alphabets (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5366">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5366">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5367">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5367">Six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5368">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5368">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5369">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5369">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5370">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5370">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5371">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5371">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5372">регулярное выражение Regex_greece_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5372">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5373">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_greece_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5373">A keyword from Keyword_greece_id_card is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5374">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5374">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5375">регулярное выражение Regex_greece_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5375">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Greece National ID Card -->
      <Entity id="82568215-1da1-46d3-874a-d2294d81b5ac" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5376">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5376">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_greece_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5377">Keyword_greece_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5377">Keyword_greece_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5378">греческий id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5378">greek id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5379">греческий национальный id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5379">greek national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5380">греческая личная id-карта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5380">greek personal id card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5381">греческий id полиции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5381">greek police id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5382">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5382">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5383">tautotita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5383">tautotita</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5384">ταυτότητα</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5384">ταυτότητα</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5385">ταυτότητας</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5385">ταυτότητας</span></span>


## <a name="greece-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5386">Номер паспорта Греции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5386">Greece passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5387">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5387">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5388">Две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5388">Two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5389">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5389">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5390">Две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5390">Two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5391">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5391">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5392">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5392">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5393">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5393">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5394">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5394">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5395">Обычное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5395">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5396">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5396">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5397">Регулярное выражение находит дату `Regex_greece_eu_passport_date` в формате DD MMM YY (Пример - 28 августа 19) или ключевое слово `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5397">The regular expression `Regex_greece_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM YY (Example - 28 Aug 19) or a keyword from `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5398">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5398">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5399">Обычное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5399">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5400">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5400">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7e65eb47-cdf9-4f52-8f90-2a27d5ee67e3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5401">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5401">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5402">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5402">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5403">паспорт #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5403">passport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5404">паспорт #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5404">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5405">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5405">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5406">паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5406">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5407">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5407">passportno</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5408">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5408">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5409">passportnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5409">passportnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5410">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5410">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5411">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5411">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5412">номера паспортов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5412">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_greece_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5413">Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5413">Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5414">αριθμός διαβατηρίου</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5414">αριθμός διαβατηρίου</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5415">αριθμούς διαβατηρίου</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5415">αριθμούς διαβατηρίου</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5416">αριθμός διαβατηριο</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5416">αριθμός διαβατηριο</span></span>


## <a name="greece-social-security-number-amka"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5417">Номер социального обеспечения Греции (AMKA)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5417">Greece Social Security Number (AMKA)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5418">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5418">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5419">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5419">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5420">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5420">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5421">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5421">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5422">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5422">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5423">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5423">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5424">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5424">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5425">11 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5425">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5426">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5426">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5427">Шесть цифр в качестве даты рождения YYMMDD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5427">Six digits as date of birth YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5428">Четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5428">Four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5429">контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5429">a check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5430">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5430">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5431">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5431">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5432">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5432">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5433">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5433">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5434">Функция находит  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5434">The function  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5435">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5435">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5436">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5436">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5437">Функция находит  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5437">The function  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Greece Social Security Number (AMKA) -->
      <Entity id="e39b03f4-50ea-41ae-af7a-a4b9539596ad" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_greece_eu_ssn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_greece_eu_ssn" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5438">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5438">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5439">Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5439">Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5440">ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5440">ssn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5441">ssn #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5441">ssn#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5442">социального обеспечения нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5442">social security no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5443">socialsecurityno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5443">socialsecurityno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5444">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5444">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5445">amka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5445">amka</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5446">a.m.k.a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5446">a.m.k.a.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5447">Αριθμού Μητρώου Κοινωνικής Ασφάλισης</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5447">Αριθμού Μητρώου Κοινωνικής Ασφάλισης</span></span>


## <a name="greece-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5448">Идентификационный номер налога в Греции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5448">Greece tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5449">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5449">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5450">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5450">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5451">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5451">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5452">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5452">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5453">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5453">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5454">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5454">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5455">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5455">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5456">Девять цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5456">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5457">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5457">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5458">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5458">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5459">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5459">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5460">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5460">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5461">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5461">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5462">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5462">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5463">Обычное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5463">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5464">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5464">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greek Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="15a54a5a-53d4-4080-ad43-a2a4fe1d3bf7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hong-kong-identity-card-hkid-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5493">Номер удостоверения личности Гонконга (HKID)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5493">Hong Kong identity card (HKID) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5494">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5494">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5495">Сочетание 8–9 букв и чисел, а также необязательные скобки вокруг последнего символа.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5495">Combination of 8-9 letters and numbers plus optional parentheses around the final character</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5496">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5496">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5497">Сочетание 8–9 букв:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5497">Combination of 8-9 letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5498">1-2 буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5498">1-2 letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5499">шесть цифр; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5499">Six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5500">последний символ (любая цифра или буква "A") является проверочной цифрой и заключен в скобки (необязательно).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5500">The final character (any digit or the letter A), which is the check digit and is optionally enclosed in parentheses.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5501">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5501">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5502">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5502">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5503">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5503">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5504">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5504">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5505">функция Func_hong_kong_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5505">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5506">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_hong_kong_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5506">A keyword from Keyword_hong_kong_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5507">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5507">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5508">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5508">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5509">функция Func_hong_kong_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5509">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5510">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5510">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Hong Kong Identity Card (HKID) number -->
<Entity id="e63c28a7-ad29-4c17-a41a-3d2a0b70fd9c" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5550">Номер водительских прав в Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5550">Hungary driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5551">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5551">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5552">Две буквы с шестью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5552">Two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5553">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5553">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5554">Две буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5554">Two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5555">Две буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5555">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5556">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5556">Six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5557">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5557">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5558">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5558">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5559">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5559">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5560">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5560">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5561">Обычное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5561">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5562">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5562">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <Entity id="9d31c46b-6e6b-444c-aeb1-6dd7e604bb24" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5687">Личный идентификационный номер Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5687">Hungary personal identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5688">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5688">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5689">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5689">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5690">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5690">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5691">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5691">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5692">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5692">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5693">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5693">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5694">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5694">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5695">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5695">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5696">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5696">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5697">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5697">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5698">Одна цифра, соответствующая полу, 1 для мужчины, 2 для женщин.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5698">One digit that corresponds to gender, 1 for male, 2 for female.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5699">Другие номера также возможны для граждан, родившихся до 1900 г. или граждан с двойным гражданством.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5699">Other numbers are also possible for citizens born before 1900 or citizens with double citizenship.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5700">Шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5700">Six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5701">Три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5701">Three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5702">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5702">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5703">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5703">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5704">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5704">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5705">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5705">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5706">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5706">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5707">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5707">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5708">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5708">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5709">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5709">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5710">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5710">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="7b5cc218-7046-47d9-80c9-f325b50896ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5711">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5711">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5712">Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5712">Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5713">номер id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5713">id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5714">identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5714">identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5715">sz ig</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5715">sz ig</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5716">sz.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5716">sz.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5717">ig.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5717">ig.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5718">sz.ig.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5718">sz.ig.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5719">személyazonosító igazolvány</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5719">személyazonosító igazolvány</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5720">személyi igazolvány</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5720">személyi igazolvány</span></span>


## <a name="hungary-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5721">Номер паспорта Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5721">Hungary passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5722">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5722">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5723">Две буквы с шестью или семью цифрами без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5723">Two letters followed by six or seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5724">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5724">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5725">Две буквы с шестью или семью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5725">Two letters followed by six or seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5726">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5726">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5727">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5727">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5728">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5728">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5729">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5729">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5730">Обычное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5730">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5731">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5731">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5732">Обычное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date` DD MMM/MMM YY (Пример - 01 MÁR/MAR 12) или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из найдено</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5732">The regular expression `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format  DD MMM/MMM YY (Example - 01 MÁR/MAR 12) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5733">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5733">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5734">Обычное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5734">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5735">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5735">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="5b483910-9aa7-4c99-9917-f4001464bda7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5736">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5736">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5737">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5737">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5741">паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5741">passports</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5745">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5745">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5746">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5746">passportnumbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5748">Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5748">Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5749">útlevél száma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5749">útlevél száma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5750">Útlevelek száma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5750">Útlevelek száma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5751">útlevél szám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5751">útlevél szám</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5753">дата выпуска</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5753">date of issue</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5754">дата истечения срока действия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5754">date of expiry</span></span>


## <a name="hungary-social-security-number-taj"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5755">Номер социального обеспечения Венгрии (TAJ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5755">Hungary social security number (TAJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5756">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5756">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5757">Девять цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5757">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5758">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5758">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5759">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5759">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5760">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5760">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5761">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5761">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5762">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5762">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5763">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5763">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5764">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5764">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5765">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5765">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5766">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5766">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5767">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5767">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Social Security Number (TAJ) -->
      <Entity id="0de78315-9537-47f5-95ab-b3e77eba3993" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5787">Идентификация налога в Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5787">Hungary tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5788">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5788">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5789">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5789">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5790">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5790">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5791">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5791">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5792">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5792">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5793">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5793">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5794">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5794">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5795">10 цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5795">10 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5796">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5796">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5797">10 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5797">10 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5798">Одна цифра, которая должна быть "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5798">One digit that must be "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5799">Восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5799">Eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5800">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5800">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5801">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5801">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5802">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5802">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5803">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5803">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5804">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5804">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5805">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5805">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5806">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5806">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5807">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5807">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5808">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5808">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="ede42eb4-59d9-49eb-9603-d7853fbda91d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5820">нет налога #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5820">tax no#</span></span>

## <a name="hungary-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5834">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость в Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5834">Hungary value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5835">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5835">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5836">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5836">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5837">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5837">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5838">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5838">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5839">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5839">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5840">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5840">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5841">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5841">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5842">Альфанумерный шаблон 10 символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5842">10 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5843">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5843">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5844">10 символов альфанумерного шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5844">10 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5845">две буквы - HU или hu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5845">two letters - HU or hu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5846">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5846">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5847">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5847">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5848">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5848">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5849">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5849">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5850">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5850">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5851">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5851">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5852">Функция Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5852">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5853">Ключевое слово Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5853">A keyword from Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5854">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5854">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5855">Функция Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5855">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="976349a0-683b-477a-90f8-ff0a220d5592" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5856">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5856">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_hungary_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5857">Keyword_Hungary_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5857">Keyword_Hungary_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5858">vat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5858">vat</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5859">номер налога на добавленную стоимость</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5859">value added tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5860">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5860">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5861">vatno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5861">vatno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5862">hungarianvatno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5862">hungarianvatno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5863">нет налога.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5863">tax no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5864">налог на добавленную стоимость áfa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5864">value added tax áfa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5865">közösségi adószám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5865">közösségi adószám</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5866">általános forgalmi adó szám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5866">általános forgalmi adó szám</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5867">hozzáadottérték adó</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5867">hozzáadottérték adó</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5868">áfa szám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5868">áfa szám</span></span>


## <a name="india-permanent-account-number-pan"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5869">Постоянный номер учетной записи Индии (PAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5869">India permanent account number (PAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5870">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5870">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5871">10 букв или цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5871">10 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5872">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5872">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5873">10 букв или цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5873">10 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5874">Три буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5874">Three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5875">Буквы C, P, H, F, A, T, B, L, J, G (не чувствительны к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5875">A letter in C, P, H, F, A, T, B, L, J, G (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5876">Письмо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5876">A letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5877">Четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5877">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5878">Буква, которая является алфавитной цифрой проверки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5878">A letter that is an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5879">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5879">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5880">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5880">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5881">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5881">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5882">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5882">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5883">регулярное выражение Regex_india_permanent_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5883">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5884">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_india_permanent_account_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5884">A keyword from Keyword_india_permanent_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5885">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5885">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5886">регулярное выражение Regex_india_permanent_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5886">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>


```xml
      <!-- India Permanent Account Number -->
      <Entity id="2602bfee-9bb0-47a5-a7a6-2bf3053e2804" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_india_permanent_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3520.000">
          <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number" />
          </Pattern>
        </Version>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5887">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5887">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_india_permanent_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5888">Keyword_india_permanent_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5888">Keyword_india_permanent_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5889">Permanent Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5889">Permanent Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5890">PAN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5890">PAN</span></span> 
   
## <a name="india-unique-identification-aadhaar-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5891">Уникальный идентификационный номер Индии (Aadhaar)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5891">India unique identification (Aadhaar) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5892">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5892">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5893">12 цифр, содержащих необязательные пробелы или тире.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5893">12 digits containing optional spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5894">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5894">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5895">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5895">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5896">Цифры, не 0 или 1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5896">A digit which is not 0 or 1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5897">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5897">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5898">необязательный пробел или тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5898">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5899">четыре цифры;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5899">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5900">необязательный пробел или тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5900">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5901">Окончательная цифра, которая является чековой цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5901">The final digit, which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5902">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5902">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5903">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5903">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5904">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5904">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5905">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5905">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5906">функция Func_india_aadhaar находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5906">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5907">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_india_aadhar;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5907">A keyword from Keyword_india_aadhar is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5908">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5908">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- 
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5909">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5909">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5910">функция Func_india_aadhaar находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5910">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5911">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5911">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- India Unique Identification (Aadhaar) number -->
<Entity id="1ca46b29-76f5-4f46-9383-cfa15e91048f" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_india_aadhar"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5912">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5912">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_india_aadhar"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5913">Keyword_india_aadhar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5913">Keyword_india_aadhar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5914">aadhaar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5914">aadhaar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5915">aadhar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5915">aadhar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5916">aadhar #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5916">aadhar#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5917">uid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5917">uid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5918">आधार</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5918">आधार</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5919">uidai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5919">uidai</span></span>
   
## <a name="indonesia-identity-card-ktp-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5920">Номер удостоверения личности (KTP) в Индонезии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5920">Indonesia identity card (KTP) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5921">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5921">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5922">16 цифр, содержащих необязательные точки.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5922">16 digits containing optional periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5923">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5923">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5924">16 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5924">16 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5925">две цифры (код провинции);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5925">Two-digit province code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5926">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5926">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5927">две цифры (код округа или города);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5927">Two-digit regency or city code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5928">две цифры (код района);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5928">Two-digit subdistrict code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5929">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5929">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5930">Шесть цифр в формате DDMMYY, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5930">Six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5931">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5931">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5932">четыре цифры.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5932">Four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5933">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5933">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5934">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5934">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5935">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5935">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5936">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5936">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5937">регулярное выражение Regex_indonesia_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5937">The regular expression Regex_indonesia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5938">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_indonesia_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5938">A keyword from Keyword_indonesia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Indonesia Identity Card (KTP) Number -->
<Entity id="da68fdb0-f383-4981-8c86-82689d3b7d55" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_indonesia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_indonesia_id_card"/>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5939">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5939">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_indonesia_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5940">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5940">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5941">KTP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5941">KTP</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5942">Kartu Tanda Penduduk</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5942">Kartu Tanda Penduduk</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5943">Nomor Induk Kependudukan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5943">Nomor Induk Kependudukan</span></span> 
   
## <a name="international-banking-account-number-iban"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5944">Номер международного банковского счета (IBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5944">International banking account number (IBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5945">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5945">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5946">Код страны (две буквы), а также проверочные цифры (две) и номер bban (до 30 символов)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5946">Country code (two letters) plus check digits (two digits) plus bban number (up to 30 characters)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5947">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5947">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5948">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5948">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5949">Двухбуквенный код страны</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5949">Two-letter country code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5950">Две проверочные цифры (после которых может следовать пробел) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5950">Two check digits (followed by an optional space)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5951">1–7 групп из четырех букв или цифр (могут разделяться пробелами)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5951">1-7 groups of four letters or digits (can be separated by spaces)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5952">1–3 буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5952">1-3 letters or digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-p139">Формат для названия каждой из стран немного отличается. Тип конфиденциальной информации IBAN применяется к следующим 60 странам:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-p139">The format for each country is slightly different. The IBAN sensitive information type covers these 60 countries:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5955">ad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5955">ad</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5956">ae</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5956">ae</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5957">al</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5957">al</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5958">в</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5958">at</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5959">az</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5959">az</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-5960">ba</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-5960">ba</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6016">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6016">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6017">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6017">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6018">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6018">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6019">функция Func_iban находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6019">The function Func_iban finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6020">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6020">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="e7dc4711-11b7-4cb0-b88b-2c394a771f0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_iban" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
