<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6022">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6022">None</span></span>

   
## <a name="international-classification-of-diseases-icd-10-cm"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6023">Международная классификация заболеваний (ICD-10-CM)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6023">International classification of diseases (ICD-10-CM)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6024">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6024">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6025">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6025">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6026">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6026">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6027">Ключевое слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6027">Keyword</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6028">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6028">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6029">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6029">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6030">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6030">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6031">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6031">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6032">Ключевое слово Dictionary_icd_10_updated найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6032">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6033">Ключевое слово Dictionary_icd_10_codes найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6033">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6034">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6034">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6035">Найдено ключевое слово Dictionary_icd_10_ обновления.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6035">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_ updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- ICD-10 CM -->
      <Entity id="3356946c-6bb7-449b-b253-6ffa419c0ce7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
        </Pattern>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6036">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6036">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6037">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_10_updated ключевого слова, который основан на международной классификации заболеваний, десятой ревизии, клинической модификации [(ICD-10-CM).](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6037">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_10_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases, Tenth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6038">Этот тип ищет только термин, а не коды страхования.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6038">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6039">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_10_codes ключевого слова, который основан на международной классификации заболеваний, десятой ревизии, клинической модификации [(ICD-10-CM).](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6039">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_10_codes keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases, Tenth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6040">Этот тип ищет только коды страхования, а не описание.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6040">This type looks only for insurance codes, not the description.</span></span>

## <a name="international-classification-of-diseases-icd-9-cm"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6041">Международная классификация заболеваний (ICD-9-CM)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6041">International classification of diseases (ICD-9-CM)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6042">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6042">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6043">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6043">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6044">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6044">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6045">Ключевое слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6045">Keyword</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6046">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6046">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6047">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6047">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6048">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6048">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6049">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6049">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6050">Ключевое слово Dictionary_icd_9_updated найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6050">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6051">Ключевое слово Dictionary_icd_9_codes найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6051">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6052">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6052">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6053">Ключевое слово Dictionary_icd_9_updated найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6053">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <Entity id="fa3f9c74-ee07-4c52-b5f2-085d6b2c0ec4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6054">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6054">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6055">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_9_updated ключевого слова, который основан на международной классификации заболеваний, девятой ревизии, клинической модификации [(ICD-9-CM).](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6055">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6056">Этот тип ищет только термин, а не коды страхования.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6056">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6057">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_9_codes ключевого слова, который основан на международной классификации болезней, девятой ревизии, клинической модификации [(ICD-9-CM).](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6057">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_codes keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6058">Этот тип ищет только коды страхования, а не описание.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6058">This type looks only for insurance codes, not the description.</span></span>

## <a name="ip-address"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6059">IP-адрес.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6059">IP address</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6060">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6060">Format</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv4"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6061">IPv4:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6061">IPv4:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6062">Сложный шаблон, который учитывает отформатированные (периоды) и неформатированные (без периодов) версии адресов IPv4</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6062">Complex pattern that accounts for formatted (periods) and unformatted (no periods) versions of the IPv4 addresses</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv6"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6063">IPv6:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6063">IPv6:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6064">Сложный шаблон, который учитывает отформатированные номера IPv6 (включая двоеточия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6064">Complex pattern that accounts for formatted IPv6 numbers (which include colons)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6065">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6065">Pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6066">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6066">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6067">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6067">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6068">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6068">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6069">Для IPv6 политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6069">For IPv6, a DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6070">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv6_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6070">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6071">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6071">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6072">Для IPv4 политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что он обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6072">For IPv4, a DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6073">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv4_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6073">The regular expression Regex_ipv4_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6074">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6074">A keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6075">Для IPv6 политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6075">For IPv6, a DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6076">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv6_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6076">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6077">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6077">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- IP Address -->
    <Entity id="1daa4ad5-e2dd-4ca4-a788-54722c09efb2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv4_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6078">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6078">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6080">IP (это ключевое слово является чувствительным к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6080">IP (this keyword is case-sensitive)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6083">internet protocol</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6083">internet protocol</span></span>

## <a name="ireland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6085">Номер лицензии водителя Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6085">Ireland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6086">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6086">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6087">Шесть цифр, за которыми следуют четыре буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6087">Six digits followed by four letters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6088">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6088">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6089">Шесть цифр и четыре буквы:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6089">Six digits and four letters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6090">Шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6090">Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6091">Четыре буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6091">Four letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6092">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6092">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6093">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6093">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6094">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6094">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6095">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6095">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6096">Обычное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6096">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6097">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6097">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Ireland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="e01bccd9-eb4d-414f-ace1-e9b6a4c4a2ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6221">Номер паспорта Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6221">Ireland passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6222">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6222">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6223">Две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6223">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6224">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6224">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6225">Две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6225">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6226">Две цифры или буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6226">Two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6227">семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6227">Seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6228">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6228">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6229">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6229">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6230">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6230">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6231">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6231">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6232">Обычное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6232">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6233">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6233">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6234">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date` DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Пример - 01 BEA/MAY 1988) или ключевое слово из `Keywords_eu_passport_date` найденного</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6234">The regular expression `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 BEA/MAY 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6235">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6235">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6236">Обычное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6236">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6237">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6237">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Ireland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="a2130f27-9ee2-4103-84f9-a6b1ee7d0cbf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-personal-public-service-pps-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6261">Номер личной государственной службы Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6261">Ireland personal public service (PPS) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6262">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6262">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6263">Старый формат (до 31 декабря 2012 г.):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6263">Old format (until 31 December 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6264">семь цифр, за которыми следуют 1-2 буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6264">seven digits followed by 1-2 letters</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6265">Новый формат (1 января 2013 г. и после):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6265">New format (1 January 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6266">семь цифр, за которыми следуют две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6266">seven digits followed by two letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6267">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6267">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6268">Старый формат (до 31 декабря 2012 г.):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6268">Old format (until 31 December 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6269">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6269">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6270">от одной до двух букв (не чувствительных к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6270">one to two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6271">Новый формат (1 января 2013 г. и после):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6271">New format (1 January 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6272">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6272">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6273">буква (не чувствительная к делу), которая является алфавитной цифрой проверки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6273">a letter (not case-sensitive) which is an alphabetic check digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6274">Необязательная буква в диапазоне A-I или "W"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6274">An optional letter in the range A-I, or “W”</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6275">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6275">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6276">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6276">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6277">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6277">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6278">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6278">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6279">функция Func_ireland_pps находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6279">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6280">Ключевое слово из Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6280">A keyword from Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6281">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6281">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6282">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6282">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6283">функция Func_ireland_pps находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6283">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6284">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6284">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ireland Personal Public Service (PPS) Number -->
      <Entity id="1cdb674d-c19a-4fcf-9f4b-7f56cc87345a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="israel-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6329">Номер банковского счета Израиля</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6329">Israel bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6330">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6330">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6331">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6331">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6332">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6332">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6333">Форматированный:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6333">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6334">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6334">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6335">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6335">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6336">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6336">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6337">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6337">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6338">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6338">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6339">Unformatted:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6339">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6340">	13 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6340">13 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6341">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6341">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6342">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6342">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6343">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6343">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6344">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6344">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6345">регулярное выражение Regex_israel_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6345">The regular expression Regex_israel_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6346">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_israel_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6346">A keyword from Keyword_israel_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="7d08b2ff-a0b9-437f-957c-aeddbf9b2b25" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_israel_bank_account_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_israel_bank_account_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6347">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6347">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_israel_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6348">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6348">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6349">Bank Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6349">Bank Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6350">Bank Account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6350">Bank Account</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6351">Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6351">Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6352">מספר חשבון בנק</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6352">מספר חשבון בנק</span></span> 
   
## <a name="israel-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6353">Национальный идентификационный номер Израиля</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6353">Israel national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6354">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6354">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6355">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6355">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6356">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6356">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6357">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6357">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6358">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6358">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6359">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6359">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6360">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6360">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6361">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6361">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6362">функция Func_israeli_national_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6362">The function Func_israeli_national_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6363">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Israel_National_ID;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6363">A keyword from Keyword_Israel_National_ID is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6364">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6364">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel National ID Number -->
<Entity id="e05881f5-1db1-418c-89aa-a3ac5c5277ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_israeli_national_id_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Israel_National_ID" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

-   <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6370">זהותישר אלית</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6370">זהותישר אלית</span></span>

-   <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6372">هوية إسرائ يلية</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6372">هوية إسرائ يلية</span></span>

-   <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6376">номер id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6376">id number</span></span>

-   <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6378">identitynumber #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6378">identitynumber#</span></span>

## <a name="italy-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6383">Номер водительских прав в Италии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6383">Italy driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6384">Этот тип объекта включен в тип конфиденциальной информации о номере лицензии водителя ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6384">This type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6385">Он также доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6385">It is also available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6386">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6386">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6387">сочетание 10 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6387">a combination of 10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6388">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6388">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6389">сочетание 10 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6389">a combination of 10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6390">одна буква (не деликатная)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6390">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6391">буквы "A" или "V" (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6391">the letter "A" or "V" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6392">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6392">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6393">одна буква (не деликатная)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6393">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6394">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6394">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6395">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6395">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6396">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6396">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6397">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6397">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6398">Обычное выражение `Regex_italy_drivers_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6398">The regular expression `Regex_italy_drivers_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6399">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6399">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- Italy Driver's license Number -->
    <Entity id="97d6244f-9157-41bd-8e0c-9d669a5c4d71" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_drivers_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-fiscal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6526">Финансовый код Италии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6526">Italy fiscal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6527">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6527">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6528">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6528">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6529">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6529">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6530">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6530">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6531">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6531">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6532">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6532">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6533">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6533">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6534">16-символьное сочетание букв и цифр в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6534">a 16-character combination of letters and digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6535">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6535">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6536">Сочетание букв и цифр в 16 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6536">A 16-character combination of letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6537">три буквы, соответствующие первым трем согласным в фамилии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6537">three letters that correspond to the first three consonants in the family name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6538">три буквы, соответствующие первому, третьему и четвертому согласным с именем</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6538">three letters that correspond to the first, third, and fourth consonants in the first name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6539">две цифры, соответствующие последним цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6539">two digits that correspond to the last digits of the birth year</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6540">в алфавитном порядке используется одна буква, соответствующая букве за месяц рождения, но используются только буквы A к E, H, L, M, P, R к T (так, январь — A и Октябрь — R)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6540">one letter that corresponds to the letter for the month of birth—letters are used in alphabetical order, but only the letters A to E, H, L, M, P, R to T are used (so, January is A and October is R)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6541">две цифры, соответствующие дню рождения, чтобы различать полы, добавляется 40 к дню рождения для женщин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6541">two digits that correspond to the day of the month of birth in order to differentiate between genders, 40 is added to the day of birth for women</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6542">четыре цифры, соответствующие коду области, определенному муниципалитету, в котором родился человек (коды по всей стране используются для иностранных стран)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6542">four digits that correspond to the area code specific to the municipality where the person was born (country-wide codes are used for foreign countries)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6543">одно число паритета</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6543">one parity digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6544">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6544">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6545">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6545">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6546">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6546">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6547">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6547">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6548">Функция находит  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6548">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6549">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6549">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6550">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6550">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6551">Функция находит  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6551">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Fiscal Code -->
      <Entity id="4cd79172-8da9-4ff5-9188-98b1e7e2eca6" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6586">Номер паспорта Италии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6586">Italy passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6587">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6587">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6588">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6588">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6589">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6589">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6590">две буквы или цифры, а затем семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6590">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6591">две цифры или буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6591">two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6592">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6592">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6593">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6593">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6594">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6594">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6595">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6595">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6596">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6596">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6597">Обычное выражение  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6597">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6598">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6598">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6599">Обычное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` DD MMM/MMM YYYYY (Пример - 01 GEN/JAN 1988) или ключевое слово из `Keywords_eu_passport_date` найденного</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6599">The regular expression `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 GEN/JAN 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6600">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6600">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6601">Обычное выражение  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6601">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6602">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6602">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="39811019-4750-445f-b26d-4c0e6c431544" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6603">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6603">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number_common"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6604">Keywords_eu_passport_number_common</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6604">Keywords_eu_passport_number_common</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6605">паспорт #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6605">passport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6606">паспорт #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6606">passport #</span></span>

## <a name="italy-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6626">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость в Италии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6626">Italy value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6627">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6627">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6628">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6628">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6629">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6629">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6630">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6630">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6631">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6631">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6632">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6632">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6633">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6633">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6634">13 символов альфанумерного шаблона с необязательными делимитерами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6634">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6635">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6635">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6636">13 символов альфанумерного шаблона с необязательными делимитерами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6636">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6637">I или i</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6637">I or i</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6638">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6638">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6639">необязательное пространство, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6639">optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6640">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6640">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6641">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6641">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6642">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6642">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6643">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6643">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6644">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6644">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6645">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6645">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6646">Найдено ключевое слово Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number из Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6646">A keyword from Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6647">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6647">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6648">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6648">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Italy Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="26a8cc07-2283-4a2a-ab1d-4ab643c4c67f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6650">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6650">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

## <a name="japan-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6656">Номер банковского счета в Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6656">Japan bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6657">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6657">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6658">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6658">seven or eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6659">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6659">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6660">Номер банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6660">bank account number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6661">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6661">seven or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6662">Код филиала банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6662">bank account branch code:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6663">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6663">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6664">пространство или тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6664">a space or dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6665">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6665">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6666">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6666">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6667">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6667">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6668">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6668">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6669">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6669">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6670">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6670">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6671">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6671">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6672">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6672">One of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6673">функция Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6673">The function Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6674">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6674">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6675">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6675">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6676">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6676">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6677">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6677">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="d354f95b-96ee-4b80-80bc-4377312b55bc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Version minEngineVersion="15.01.0131.000">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
  </Version>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6725">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6725">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6726">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6726">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6727">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6727">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6728">12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6728">12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6729">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6729">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6730">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6730">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6731">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6731">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6732">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6732">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6733">функция Func_jp_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6733">The function Func_jp_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6734">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6734">A keyword from Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="c6011143-d087-451c-8313-7f6d4aed2270" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-my-number---corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6772">Япония Мой номер — корпоративная</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6772">Japan My Number - Corporate</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6773">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6773">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6774">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6774">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6775">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6775">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6776">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6776">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6777">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6777">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6778">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6778">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6779">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6779">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6780">13-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6780">13-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6781">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6781">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6782">13-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6782">13-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6783">одна цифра от одной до девяти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6783">one digit from one to nine</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6784">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6784">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6785">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6785">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6786">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6786">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6787">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6787">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6788">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6788">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6789">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6789">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6790">Ключевое слово Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6790">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6791">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6791">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6792">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6792">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Corporate -->
      <Entity id="9e0eaf79-ff20-4ffb-b3e4-e7368d5db6ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6795">корпоративный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6795">corporate number</span></span>
