## <a name="japan-my-number---personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6805">Япония Мой номер - Личный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6805">Japan My Number - Personal</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6806">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6806">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6807">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6807">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6808">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6808">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6809">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6809">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6810">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6810">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6811">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6811">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6812">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6812">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6813">12-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6813">12-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6814">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6814">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6815">12-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6815">12-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6816">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6816">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6817">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6817">an optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6818">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6818">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6819">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6819">an optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6820">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6820">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6821">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6821">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6822">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6822">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6823">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6823">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6824">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6824">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6825">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6825">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6826">Ключевое слово Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6826">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6827">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6827">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6828">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6828">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Personal -->
      <Entity id="98da8e66-7299-4ebd-9f82-c871ab37d3ef" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6829">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6829">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_japan_my_number_personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6830">Keyword_japan_my_number_personal</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6830">Keyword_japan_my_number_personal</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6831">мой номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6831">my number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6832">マイナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6832">マイナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6833">個人番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6833">個人番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6834">共通番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6834">共通番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6835">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6835">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6836">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6836">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6837">個人番号カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6837">個人番号カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6838">個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6838">個人識別番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6839">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6839">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6840">通知カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6840">通知カード</span></span>

   
## <a name="japan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6841">Номер паспорта Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6841">Japan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6842">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6842">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6843">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6843">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6844">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6844">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6845">две буквы (не чувствительные к делу), за которыми следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6845">two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6846">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6846">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6847">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6847">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6848">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6848">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6849">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6849">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6850">функция Func_jp_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6850">The function Func_jp_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6851">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6851">A keyword from Keyword_jp_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="75177310-1a09-4613-bf6d-833aae3743f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6852">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6852">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6853">Keyword_jp_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6853">Keyword_jp_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6854">Паспорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6854">Passport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6855">Passport Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6855">Passport Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6856">Паспорт No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6856">Passport No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6857">Passport#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6857">Passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6858">パスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6858">パスポート</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6859">パスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6859">パスポート番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6860">パスポートナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6860">パスポートナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6861">パスポート＃</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6861">パスポート＃</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6862">パスポート #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6862">パスポート#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6863">パポ.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6863">パスポートNo.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6864">旅券番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6864">旅券番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6865">旅券番号＃</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6865">旅券番号＃</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6866">旅券番号♯</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6866">旅券番号♯</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6867">旅券ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6867">旅券ナンバー</span></span>


## <a name="japan-residence-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6868">Номер карты проживания в Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6868">Japan residence card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6869">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6869">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6870">12 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6870">12 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6871">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6871">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6872">12 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6872">12 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6873">две буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6873">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6874">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6874">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6875">две буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6875">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6876">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6876">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6877">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6877">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6878">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6878">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6879">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6879">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6880">Регулярное выражение Regex_jp_residence_card_number контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6880">The regular expression Regex_jp_residence_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6881">Ключевое слово Keyword_jp_residence_card_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6881">A keyword from Keyword_jp_residence_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Japan Residence Card Number-->
-<Entity id="ac36fef2-a289-4e2c-bb48-b02366e89fc0" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_jp_residence_card_number"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_residence_card_number"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6882">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6882">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_residence_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6883">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6883">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6884">Номер карточки residence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6884">Residence card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6885">Карточка residence no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6885">Residence card no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6886">Карточка residence #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6886">Residence card #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6887">在留カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6887">在留カード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6888">在留カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6888">在留カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6889">在留番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6889">在留番号</span></span>

## <a name="japan-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6890">Регистрационный номер резидента Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6890">Japan resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6891">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6891">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6892">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6892">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6893">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6893">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6894">11 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6894">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6895">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6895">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6896">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6896">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6897">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6897">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6898">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6898">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6899">функция Func_jp_resident_registration_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6899">The function Func_jp_resident_registration_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6900">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6900">A keyword from Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="01c1209b-6389-4faf-a5f8-3f7e13899652" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_resident_registration_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6901">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6901">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_resident_registration_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6902">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6902">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6903">Resident Registration Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6903">Resident Registration Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6904">Residents Basic Registry Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6904">Residents Basic Registry Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6905">Resident Registration No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6905">Resident Registration No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6906">Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6906">Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6907">Residents Basic Registry No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6907">Residents Basic Registry No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6908">Basic Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6908">Basic Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6909">外国人登録証明書番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6909">外国人登録証明書番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6910">証明書番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6910">証明書番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6911">登録番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6911">登録番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6912">外国人登録証</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6912">外国人登録証</span></span>

   
## <a name="japan-social-insurance-number-sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6913">Номер социального страхования Японии (SIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6913">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6914">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6914">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6915">7–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6915">7-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6916">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6916">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6917">7–12 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6917">7-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6918">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6918">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6919">дефис (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6919">a hyphen (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6920">шесть цифр OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6920">six digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6921">7–12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6921">7-12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6922">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6922">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6923">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6923">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6924">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6924">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6925">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6925">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6926">функция Func_jp_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6926">The function Func_jp_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6927">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6927">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6928">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6928">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6929">функция Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6929">The function Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6930">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6930">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="c840e719-0896-45bb-84fd-1ed5c95e45ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin_pre_1997" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="latvia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6951">Номер водительских прав в Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6951">Latvia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6952">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6952">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6953">три буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6953">three letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6954">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6954">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6955">три буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6955">three letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6956">три буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6956">three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6957">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6957">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6958">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6958">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6959">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6959">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6960">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6960">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6961">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6961">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6962">Обычное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6962">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-6963">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-6963">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="ec996de0-30f2-46b1-b192-4d2ff8805fa7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="latvia-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7088">Персональный код Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7088">Latvia personal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7089">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7089">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7090">11 цифр и необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7090">11 digits and an optional hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7091">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7091">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7092">Старый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7092">Old format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7093">11 цифр и дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7093">11 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7094">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (DDMMYY)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7094">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7095">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7095">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7096">одна цифра, соответствующая столетию рождения ("0" для 19-го века, "1" для 20-го века и "2" для 21-го века)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7096">one digit that corresponds to the century of birth ("0" for 19th century, "1" for 20th century, and "2" for 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7097">четыре цифры, случайно созданные</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7097">four digits, randomly generated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7098">Новый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7098">New format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7099">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7099">11 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7100">Две цифры "32"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7100">Two digits "32"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7101">девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7101">Nine digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7102">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7102">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7103">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7103">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7104">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7104">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7105">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7105">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7106">Функция или  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` regex находит `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7106">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7107">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7107">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7108">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7108">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7109">Функция или  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` regex находит `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7109">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="03fcf763-27c2-49ed-9422-2641c6c895c9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="latvia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7172">Номер паспорта Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7172">Latvia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7173">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7173">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7174">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7174">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7175">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7175">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7176">две буквы или цифры, а затем семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7176">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7177">две цифры или буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7177">two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7178">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7178">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7179">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7179">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7180">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7180">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7181">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7181">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7182">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7182">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7183">Обычное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7183">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7184">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7184">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7185">Обычное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате DD.MM.YYYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7185">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7186">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7186">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7187">Обычное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7187">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7188">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7188">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="23ae25ec-cc28-421b-b77a-3054eadf1ede" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7211">Номер водительских прав Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7211">Lithuania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7212">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7212">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7213">восемь цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7213">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7214">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7214">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7215">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7215">eight digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7216">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7216">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7217">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7217">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7218">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7218">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7219">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7219">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7220">Обычное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7220">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7221">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7221">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="86f7628b-e0f4-4dc3-9fbc-e4300e4c7d78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7346">Личный код Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7346">Lithuania personal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7347">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7347">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7348">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7348">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7349">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7349">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7350">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7350">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7351">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7351">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7352">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7352">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7353">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7353">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7354">11 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7354">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7355">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7355">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7356">11 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7356">11 digits without spaces and delimiters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7357">одна цифра (1-6), соответствующая полу и столетию рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7357">one digit (1-6) that corresponds to the person's gender and century of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7358">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7358">six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7359">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру даты рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7359">three digits that correspond to the serial number of the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7360">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7360">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7361">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7361">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7362">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7362">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7363">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7363">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7364">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7364">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7365">Функция находит  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7365">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7366">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7366">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7367">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7367">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7368">Функция находит  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7368">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="cd6d3786-8ec3-4524-a2cf-1e0095379171" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">

          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7403">Номер паспорта Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7403">Lithuania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7404">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7404">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7405">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7405">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7406">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7406">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7407">восемь цифр или букв (не чувствительных к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7407">eight digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7408">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7408">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7409">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7409">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7410">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7410">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7411">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7411">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7412">Обычное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7412">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7413">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7413">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7414">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date3` находит дату в формате DD MM YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7414">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7415">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7415">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7416">Обычное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7416">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7417">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7417">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1b79900f-047b-4c3f-846f-7d73b5534bce" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7437">Номер водительских прав в Люксембурге</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7437">Luxemburg driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7438">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7438">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7439">шесть цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7439">six digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7440">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7440">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7441">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7441">six digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7442">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7442">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7443">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7443">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7444">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7444">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7445">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7445">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7446">Обычное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7446">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7447">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7447">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="89daf717-1544-4860-9a2e-fc9166dd8852" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7571">Национальный идентификационный номер Люксембурга (естественные лица)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7571">Luxemburg national identification number (natural persons)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7572">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7572">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7573">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7573">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7574">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7574">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7575">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7575">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7576">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7576">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7577">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7577">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7578">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7578">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7579">13 цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7579">13 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7580">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7580">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7581">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7581">13 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7582">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7582">11 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7583">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7583">two check digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7584">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7584">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7585">да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7585">yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7586">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7586">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7587">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7587">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7588">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7588">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7589">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7589">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7590">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7590">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7591">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7591">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 


```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="aaf661ed-29ec-426d-8bf9-880cad298ebb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7614">Номер паспорта Люксембурга</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7614">Luxemburg passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7615">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7615">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7616">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7616">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7617">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7617">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7618">восемь цифр или букв (не чувствительных к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7618">eight digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7619">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7619">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7620">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7620">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7621">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7621">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7622">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7622">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7623">Обычное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7623">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7624">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7624">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7625">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date3` находит дату в формате DD MM YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7625">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7626">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7626">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7627">Обычное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7627">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7628">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7628">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="81d5c027-bed9-4421-91a0-3b2e55b3eb85" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-non-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7660">Номер национальной идентификации в Люксембурге (не естественное лицо)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7660">Luxemburg national identification number (non-natural persons)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7661">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7661">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7662">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7662">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7663">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7663">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7664">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7664">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7665">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7665">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7666">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7666">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7667">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7667">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7668">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7668">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7669">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7669">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7670">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7670">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7671">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7671">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7672">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7672">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7673">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7673">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7674">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7674">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7675">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7675">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7676">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7676">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7677">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7677">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7678">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7678">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7679">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7679">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7680">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7680">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Non-natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="84bffa3a-d805-4788-a613-b1e4df3804cf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7681">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7681">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7689">numéro d'identification fiscal luxembourgeois</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7689">numéro d'identification fiscal luxembourgeois</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7690">numéro d'identification fiscale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7690">numéro d'identification fiscale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7691">social security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7691">social security</span></span>

## <a name="malaysia-identification-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7720">Номер удостоверения личности Малайзии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7720">Malaysia identification card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7721">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7721">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7722">12 цифр, содержащих необязательные дефисы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7722">12 digits containing optional hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7723">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7723">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7724">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7724">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7725">шесть цифр в формате YYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7725">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7726">тире (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7726">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7727">двух-буквный код места рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7727">two-letter place-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7728">тире (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7728">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7729">три случайных цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7729">three random digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7730">однозначный гендерный код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7730">one-digit gender code</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7731">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7731">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7732">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7732">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7733">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7733">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7734">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7734">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7735">регулярное выражение Regex_malaysia_id_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7735">The regular expression Regex_malaysia_id_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7736">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7736">A keyword from Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Malaysia ID Card Number -->
</Entity>
      <Entity id="7f0e921c-9677-435b-aba2-bb8f1013c749" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malaysia_id_card_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7763">Номер водительского удостоверения Мальты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7763">Malta driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7764">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7764">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7765">Сочетание двух символов и шести цифр в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7765">Combination of two characters and six digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7766">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7766">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7767">сочетание двух символов и шести цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7767">combination of two characters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7768">два символа (цифры или буквы, не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7768">two characters (digits or letters, not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7769">пробел (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7769">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7770">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7770">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7771">пробел (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7771">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7772">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7772">three digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7773">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7773">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7774">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7774">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7775">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7775">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7776">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7776">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7777">Обычное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7777">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7778">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7778">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="a3bdaa4a-8371-4735-8fa5-56ee0fb4afc4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
