- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7901">liċenzji tas-sewwieq</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7901">liċenzji tas-sewwieq</span></span>


## <a name="malta-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7902">Номер удостоверения личности Мальты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7902">Malta identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7903">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7903">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7904">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7904">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7905">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7905">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7906">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7906">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7907">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7907">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7908">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7908">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7909">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7909">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7910">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7910">seven digits followed by one letter</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7911">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7911">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7912">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7912">seven digits followed by one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7913">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7913">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7914">одна буква в "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (случай нечувствительный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7914">one letter in "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (case insensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7915">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7915">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7916">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7916">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7917">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7917">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7918">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7918">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7919">Обычное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7919">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7920">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7920">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7921">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7921">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7922">Обычное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7922">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Identity Card Number -->
      <Entity id="854b36b3-a388-4ac8-a4ec-677c2b5e4356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7923">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7923">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7924">Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7924">Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7925">номер службы гражданина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7925">citizen service number</span></span>

## <a name="malta-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7939">Номер паспорта Мальты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7939">Malta passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7940">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7940">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7941">семь цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7941">seven digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7942">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7942">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7943">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7943">seven digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7944">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7944">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7945">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7945">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7946">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7946">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7947">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7947">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7948">Обычное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7948">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7949">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7949">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7950">Найдено `Keywords_eu_passport_date` ключевое слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7950">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7951">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7951">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7952">Обычное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7952">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7953">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7953">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="b2b21198-48f9-4d13-b2a5-03969bff0fb8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7973">Номер идентификации налога На Мальте</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7973">Malta tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7974">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7974">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7975">Для граждан Мальты:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7975">For Maltese nationals:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7976">семь цифр и одна буква в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7976">seven digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7977">Не мальтийские граждане и мальтийские юридические лица:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7977">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7978">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7978">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7979">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7979">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7980">Граждане Мальты: семь цифр и одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7980">Maltese nationals: seven digits and one letter</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7981">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7981">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7982">одна буква (не деликатная)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7982">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7983">Не мальтийские граждане и мальтийские сущностями: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7983">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities: nine digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7984">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7984">nine digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7985">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7985">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7986">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7986">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7987">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7987">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7988">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7988">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7989">Regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7989">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7990">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7990">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7991">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7991">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-7992">Regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-7992">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Tax ID Number -->
      <Entity id="ec830c63-65f4-45d0-9d8c-910dc8334b20" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8005">личный числимый код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8005">personal numeric code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8021">олово #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8021">tin#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8023">уникальный номер удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8023">unique identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8024">uniqueidentityno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8024">uniqueidentityno#</span></span>


## <a name="medicare-beneficiary-identifier-mbi-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8025">Идентификатор бенефициара Medicare (MBI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8025">Medicare Beneficiary Identifier (MBI) card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8026">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8026">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8027">Альфанумерный шаблон 11 символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8027">11 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8028">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8028">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8029">одна цифра от 1 до 9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8029">one digit between 1 to 9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8030">одна буква, за исключением S, L, O, I, B, Z</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8030">one letter excluding  S, L, O, I, B, Z</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8031">одна цифра или буква, за исключением S, L, O, I, B, Z</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8031">one digit or letter excluding S, L, O, I, B, Z</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8032">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8032">one digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8033">необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8033">an optional Hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8034">одна буква, за исключением S, L, O, I, B, Z</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8034">one letter excluding  S, L, O, I, B, Z</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8035">одна цифра или буква, за исключением S, L, O, I, B, Z</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8035">one digit or letter excluding S, L, O, I, B, Z</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8036">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8036">one digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8037">необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8037">an optional Hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8038">две буквы, за исключением S, L, O, I, B, Z</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8038">two letters excluding  S, L, O, I, B, Z</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8039">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8039">two digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8040">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8040">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8041">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8041">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8042">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8042">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8043">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8043">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8044">Обычное выражение  `Regex_mbi_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8044">The regular expression  `Regex_mbi_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8045">Найдено ключевое  `Keyword_mbi_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8045">A keyword from  `Keyword_mbi_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8046">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8046">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8047">Обычное выражение  `Regex_mbi_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8047">The regular expression  `Regex_mbi_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
    <!-- Medicare Beneficiary Identifier (MBI) card -->
      <Entity id="f753a286-f5cc-47e6-a592-4be25fd02591" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_mbi_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_mbi_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_mbi_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8048">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8048">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_mbi_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8049">Keyword_mbi_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8049">Keyword_mbi_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8050">mbi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8050">mbi</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8051">mbi #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8051">mbi#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8052">получатель medicare #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8052">medicare beneficiary #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8053">идентификатор бенефициара medicare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8053">medicare beneficiary identifier</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8054">получателя medicare нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8054">medicare beneficiary no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8055">номер получателя medicare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8055">medicare beneficiary number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8056">получатель medicare #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8056">medicare beneficiary#</span></span>


## <a name="mexico-unique-population-registry-code-curp"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8057">Код реестра уникальных популяций Мексики (CURP)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8057">Mexico Unique Population Registry Code (CURP)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8058">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8058">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8059">Альфанумерный шаблон 18 символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8059">18 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8060">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8060">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8061">четыре буквы (случай нечувствительный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8061">four letters (case insensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8062">шесть цифр с указанием допустимой даты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8062">six digits indicating a valid date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8063">письмо - H/h или M/m</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8063">a letter - H/h or M/m</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8064">два буквы, указывающие допустимый мексиканский код состояния</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8064">two letters indicating a valid Mexican state code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8065">три буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8065">three letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8066">одна буква или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8066">one letter or digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8067">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8067">one digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8068">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8068">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8069">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8069">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8070">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8070">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8071">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8071">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8072">Функция находит  `Func_mexico_population_registry_code` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8072">The function  `Func_mexico_population_registry_code` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8073">Найдено ключевое  `Keyword_mexico_population_registry_code` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8073">A keyword from  `Keyword_mexico_population_registry_code` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8074">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8074">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8075">Функция находит  `Func_mexico_population_registry_code` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8075">The function  `Func_mexico_population_registry_code` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
    <!-- Mexico Unique Population Registry Code (CURP) -->
      <Entity id="e905ad4d-5a74-406d-bf36-b1efca798af4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_mexico_population_registry_code" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_mexico_population_registry_code" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_mexico_population_registry_code" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8076">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8076">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_mexico_population_registry_code"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8077">Keyword_mexico_population_registry_code</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8077">Keyword_mexico_population_registry_code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8078">Clave Única de Registro de Población</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8078">Clave Única de Registro de Población</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8079">Clave Unica de Registro de Poblacion</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8079">Clave Unica de Registro de Poblacion</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8080">Уникальный код реестра населения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8080">Unique Population Registry Code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8081">уникальный код населения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8081">unique population code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8082">CURP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8082">CURP</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8083">Личный ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8083">Personal ID</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8084">Уникальный ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8084">Unique ID</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8085">personalid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8085">personalid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8086">personalidnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8086">personalidnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8087">uniqueidkey</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8087">uniqueidkey</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8088">uniqueidnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8088">uniqueidnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8089">clave única</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8089">clave única</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8090">clave unica</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8090">clave unica</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8091">clave personal Identidad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8091">clave personal Identidad</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8092">личный Identidad Clave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8092">personal Identidad Clave</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8093">ClaveÚnica</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8093">ClaveÚnica</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8094">claveunica</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8094">claveunica</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8095">clavepersonalIdentidad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8095">clavepersonalIdentidad</span></span>


## <a name="netherlands-citizens-service-bsn-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8096">Номер службы гражданина Нидерландов (BSN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8096">Netherlands citizen's service (BSN) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8097">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8097">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8098">восемь или девять цифр, содержащих необязательные пробелы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8098">eight or nine digits containing optional spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8099">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8099">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8100">восемь-девять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8100">eight-nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8101">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8101">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8102">пробел (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8102">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8103">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8103">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8104">пробел (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8104">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8105">две-три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8105">two-three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8106">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8106">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8107">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8107">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8108">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8108">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8109">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8109">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8110">функция Func_netherlands_bsn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8110">The function Func_netherlands_bsn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8111">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_netherlands_bsn;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8111">A keyword from Keyword_netherlands_bsn is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8112">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8112">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Citizen's Service (BSN) Number -->
      <Entity id="c5f54253-ef7e-44f6-a578-440ed67e946d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_bsn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8113">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8113">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8114">Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8114">Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8115">bsn #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8115">bsn#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8116">bsn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8116">bsn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8117">burgerservicenummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8117">burgerservicenummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8118">номер службы гражданина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8118">citizen service number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8119">номер лица</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8119">person number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8120">личный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8120">personal number</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8136">Номер водительских прав Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8136">Netherlands driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8137">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8137">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8138">10 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8138">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8139">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8139">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8140">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8140">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8141">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8141">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8142">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8142">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8143">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8143">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8144">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8144">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8145">Обычное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8145">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8146">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8146">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="6247fbea-ab80-4be5-8233-308b7c031401" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8274">Номер паспорта Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8274">Netherlands passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8275">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8275">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8276">девять букв или цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8276">nine letters or digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8277">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8277">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8278">девять букв или цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8278">nine letters or digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8279">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8279">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8280">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8280">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8281">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8281">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8282">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8282">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8283">Обычное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8283">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8284">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8284">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8285">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Пример - 26 MAA/MAR 2012)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8285">The regular expression `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format  DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 26 MAA/MAR 2012)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8286">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8286">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8287">Обычное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8287">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8288">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8288">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="61786727-bafd-45f6-94d9-888d815e228e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8306">Номер налоговой идентификации в Нидерландах</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8306">Netherlands tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8307">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8307">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8308">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8308">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8309">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8309">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8310">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8310">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8311">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8311">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8312">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8312">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8313">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8313">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8314">девять цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8314">nine digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8315">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8315">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8316">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8316">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8317">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8317">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8318">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8318">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8319">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8319">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8320">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8320">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8321">Функция находит  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8321">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8322">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8322">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8323">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8323">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8324">Функция находит  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8324">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="01f42a64-eba7-4892-a67b-398237e4ade2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8348">нет налога #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8348">tax no#</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8362">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость в Нидерландах</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8362">Netherlands value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8363">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8363">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8364">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8364">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8365">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8365">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8366">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8366">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8367">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8367">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8368">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8368">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8369">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8369">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8370">Альфанумерный шаблон 14 символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8370">14 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8371">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8371">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8372">14-символический альфанумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8372">14-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8373">N или n</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8373">N or n</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8374">L или l</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8374">L or l</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8375">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8375">optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8376">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8376">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8377">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8377">optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8378">B или b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8378">B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8379">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8379">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8380">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8380">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8381">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8381">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8382">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8382">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8383">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8383">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8384">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8384">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8385">Найдено ключевое слово Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8385">A keyword from Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8386">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8386">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8387">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8387">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="4f320d9b-4972-41ae-b337-88d499bb1ade" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8388">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8388">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_netherlands_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8389">Keyword_netherlands_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8389">Keyword_netherlands_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8390">номер НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8390">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8391">vat no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8391">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8392">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8392">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8393">wearde tafoege tax getal</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8393">wearde tafoege tax getal</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8394">btw nūmer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8394">btw nûmer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8395">btw-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8395">btw-nummer</span></span>


## <a name="new-zealand-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8396">Номер банковского счета в Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8396">New Zealand bank account number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8397">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8397">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8398">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8398">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8399">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8399">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8400">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8400">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8401">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8401">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8402">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8402">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8403">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8403">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8404">14-значный и 16-значный шаблон с необязательным делимитером</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8404">14-digit to 16-digit pattern with optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8405">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8405">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8406">14-значный и 16-значный шаблон с необязательным делимитером:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8406">14-digit to 16-digit pattern with optional delimiter:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8407">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8407">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8408">необязательный дефис или пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8408">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8409">три-четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8409">three to four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8410">необязательный дефис или пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8410">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8411">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8411">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8412">необязательный дефис или пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8412">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8413">две-три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8413">two to three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8414">дефис параметров или пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8414">an options hyphen or space</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8415">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8415">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8416">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8416">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8417">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8417">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8418">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8418">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8419">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8419">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8420">Ключевое слово Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8420">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8421">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8421">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8422">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8422">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Bank Account Number -->
      <Entity id="1a97fc2b-dd2f-48f1-bc4e-2ddf25813956" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zFealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8423">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8423">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8424">Keyword_new_zealand_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8424">Keyword_new_zealand_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8425">account number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8425">account number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8427">bank_acct_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8427">bank_acct_id</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8430">Номер водительского удостоверения Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8430">New Zealand driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8431">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8431">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8432">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8432">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8433">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8433">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8434">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8434">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8435">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8435">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8436">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8436">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8437">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8437">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8438">восемь шаблонов альфа-цифр символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8438">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8439">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8439">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8440">восемь шаблонов альфа-цифр символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8440">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8441">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8441">two letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8442">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8442">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8443">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8443">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8444">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8444">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8445">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8445">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8446">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8446">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8447">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8447">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8448">Ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8448">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8449">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8449">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8450">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8450">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">

        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-inland-revenue-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8517">Число внутренних доходов Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8517">New Zealand inland revenue number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8518">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8518">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8519">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8519">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8520">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8520">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8521">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8521">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8522">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8522">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8523">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8523">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8524">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8524">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8525">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными делимитерами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8525">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8526">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8526">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8527">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными делимитерами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8527">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8528">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8528">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8529">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8529">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8530">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8530">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8531">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8531">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8532">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8532">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8533">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8533">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8534">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8534">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8535">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8535">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8536">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8536">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8537">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8537">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8538">Ключевое слово Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8538">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8539">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8539">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8540">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8540">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Inland Revenue Number -->
      <Entity id="dd0fe2bc-7bcf-455f-bac1-83b1e3eb25fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8542">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8542">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span></span>
