## <a name="new-zealand-ministry-of-health-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8549">Номер министерства здравоохранения Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8549">New Zealand ministry of health number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8550">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8550">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8551">три буквы, пространство (необязательно) и четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8551">three letters, a space (optional), and four digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8552">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8552">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8553">три буквы (не чувствительные к делу), кроме "I" и "O"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8553">three letters (not case-sensitive) except 'I' and 'O'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8554">пробел (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8554">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8555">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8555">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8556">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8556">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8557">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8557">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8558">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8558">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8559">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8559">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8560">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8560">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8561">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_nz_terms;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8561">A keyword from Keyword_nz_terms is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8562">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8562">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8563">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8563">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8564">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8564">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8565">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8565">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- New Zealand Health Number -->
    <Entity id="2b71c1c8-d14e-4430-82dc-fd1ed6bf05c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_nz_terms" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
       </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8566">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8566">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_nz_terms"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8567">Keyword_nz_terms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8567">Keyword_nz_terms</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8568">NHI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8568">NHI</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8569">Новая Зеландия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8569">New Zealand</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8570">Здравоохранение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8570">Health</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8571">обработка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8571">treatment</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8572">Номер национального индекса здоровья</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8572">National Health Index Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8573">nhi number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8573">nhi number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8574">nhi нет.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8574">nhi no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8575">NHI #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8575">NHI#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8576">Национальный индекс здоровья No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8576">National Health Index No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8577">Национальный индекс здоровья</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8577">National Health Index Id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8578">Национальный индекс здоровья #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8578">National Health Index #</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-social-welfare-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8579">Номер социального обеспечения в Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8579">New Zealand social welfare number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8580">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8580">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8581">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8581">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8582">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8582">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8583">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8583">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8584">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8584">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8585">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8585">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8586">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8586">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8587">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8587">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8588">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8588">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8589">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8589">nine digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8590">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8590">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8591">необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8591">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8592">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8592">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8593">необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8593">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8594">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8594">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8595">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8595">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8596">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8596">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8597">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8597">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8598">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8598">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8599">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8599">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8600">Ключевое слово Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8600">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8601">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8601">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8602">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8602">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Newzealand Social Welfare Number -->
      <Entity id="20f3c48d-4ac1-4cd2-86bd-34ecc1826e9d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8603">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8603">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8604">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8604">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8605">социальное обеспечение #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8605">social welfare #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8606">социальное обеспечение #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8606">social welfare#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8607">No социального обеспечения.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8607">social welfare No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8608">номер социального обеспечения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8608">social welfare number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8609">swn #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8609">swn#</span></span>

   
## <a name="norway-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8610">Идентификационный номер Норвегии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8610">Norway identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8611">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8611">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8612">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8612">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8613">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8613">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8614">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8614">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8615">шесть цифр в формате DDMMYY, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8615">six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8616">трехзначный индивидуальный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8616">three-digit individual number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8617">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8617">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8618">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8618">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8619">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8619">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8620">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8620">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8621">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8621">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8622">функция Func_norway_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8622">The function Func_norway_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8623">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_norway_id_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8623">A keyword from Keyword_norway_id_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8624">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8624">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8625">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8625">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8626">функция Func_norway_id_numbe находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8626">The function Func_norway_id_numbe finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8627">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8627">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Norway Identification Number -->
<Entity id="d4c8a798-e9f2-4bd3-9652-500d24080fc3" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8628">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8628">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_norway_id_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8629">Keyword_norway_id_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8629">Keyword_norway_id_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8630">Personal identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8630">Personal identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8631">Norwegian ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8631">Norwegian ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8632">ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8632">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8633">Идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8633">Identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8634">Personnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8634">Personnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8635">Fødselsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8635">Fødselsnummer</span></span>

   
## <a name="philippines-unified-multi-purpose-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8636">Филиппины единый многоцелевой идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8636">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8637">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8637">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8638">12 цифр, разделенных дефисами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8638">12 digits separated by hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8639">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8639">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8640">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8640">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8641">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8641">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8642">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8642">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8643">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8643">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8644">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8644">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8645">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8645">one digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8646">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8646">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8647">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8647">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8648">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8648">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8649">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8649">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8650">регулярное выражение Regex_philippines_unified_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8650">The regular expression Regex_philippines_unified_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8651">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_philippines_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8651">A keyword from Keyword_philippines_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Philippines Unified Multi-Purpose ID number -->
<Entity id="019b39dd-8c25-4765-91a3-d9c6baf3c3b3" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_philippines_unified_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_philippines_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8658">Номер водительских прав в Польше</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8658">Poland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8659">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8659">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8660">14 цифр, содержащих две косые черты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8660">14 digits containing two forward slashes</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8661">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8661">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8662">14 цифр и две косые черты:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8662">14 digits and two forward slashes:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8663">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8663">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8664">перенарезаемая косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8664">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8665">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8665">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8666">перенарезаемая косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8666">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8667">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8667">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8668">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8668">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8669">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8669">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8670">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8670">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8671">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8671">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8672">Обычное выражение  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8672">The regular expression  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8673">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8673">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Poland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="24d51f99-ee9e-4060-a077-cae58cab1ee4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8797">Удостоверение личности в Польше</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8797">Poland identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8798">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8798">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8799">три буквы и шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8799">three letters and six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8800">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8800">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8801">три буквы (не чувствительные к делу) с последующим шестью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8801">three letters (not case-sensitive) followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8802">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8802">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8803">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8803">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8804">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8804">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8805">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8805">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8806">функция Func_polish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8806">The function Func_polish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8807">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8807">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8808">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8808">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Identity Card-->
<Entity id="25E64989-ED5D-40CA-A939-6C14183BB7BF" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8809">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8809">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8810">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8810">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8811">Особист dowód</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8811">Dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8812">Numer dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8812">Numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8813">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8813">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8814">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8814">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8815">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8815">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8816">Dowód Tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8816">Dowód Tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-p145">dow. os.
</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-p145">dow. os.</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-national-id-pesel"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8819">Польский национальный ID (PESEL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8819">Poland national ID (PESEL)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8820">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8820">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8821">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8821">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8822">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8822">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8823">шесть цифр, представляющих дату рождения в формате YYMMDD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8823">six digits representing date of birth in the format YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8824">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8824">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8825">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8825">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8826">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8826">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8827">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8827">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8828">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8828">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8829">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8829">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8830">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8830">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8831">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_pesel_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8831">A keyword from Keyword_pesel_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8832">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8832">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8833">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8833">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8834">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8834">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8835">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8835">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland National ID (PESEL) -->
      <Entity id="E3AAF206-4297-412F-9E06-BA8487E22456" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8836">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8836">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_pesel_identification_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8837">Keyword_pesel_identification_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8837">Keyword_pesel_identification_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8838">dowód osobisty</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8838">dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8839">dowódosobisty</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8839">dowódosobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8840">niepowtarzalny numer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8840">niepowtarzalny numer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8841">niepowtarzalnynumer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8841">niepowtarzalnynumer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8842">nr.-pesel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8842">nr.-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8843">nr-pesel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8843">nr-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8844">numer identyfikacyjny</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8844">numer identyfikacyjny</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8845">pesel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8845">pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8846">tożsamości narodowej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8846">tożsamości narodowej</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8847">Номер паспорта Польши</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8847">Poland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8848">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации входит в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8848">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8849">Он также доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8849">It's also available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8850">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8850">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8851">две буквы и семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8851">two letters and seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8852">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8852">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8853">Две буквы (не чувствительные к делу) с семью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8853">Two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8854">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8854">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8855">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8855">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8856">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8856">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8857">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8857">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8858">Функция находит `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8858">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8859">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8859">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8860">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8860">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8861">Найдено ключевое `Keywords_eu_passport_date` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8861">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8862">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8862">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8863">Функция находит `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8863">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8864">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8864">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8865">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8865">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8866">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8866">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8867">Функция находит `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8867">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8868">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8868">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="03937FB5-D2B6-4487-B61F-0F8BFF7C3517" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8869">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8869">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8870">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8870">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

## <a name="poland-regon-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8894">Номер REGON в Польше</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8894">Poland REGON number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8895">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8895">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8896">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8896">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8897">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8897">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8898">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8898">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8899">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8899">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8900">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8900">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8901">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8901">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8902">9-значный или 14-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8902">9-digit or 14-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8903">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8903">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8904">девять цифр или 14-значное число:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8904">nine digit or 14-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8905">девять цифр или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8905">nine digits or</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8906">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8906">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8907">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8907">hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8908">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8908">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8909">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8909">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8910">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8910">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8911">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8911">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8912">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8912">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8913">Функция Func_polish_regon_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8913">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8914">Ключевое слово Keywords_polish_regon_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8914">A keyword from Keywords_polish_regon_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8915">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8915">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8916">Функция Func_polish_regon_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8916">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Polish REGON Number  -->
      <Entity id="fc87b421-f437-4f8b-b739-29a735ead0d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8922">статистический нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8922">statistical no</span></span>

## <a name="poland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8933">Номер налоговой идентификации в Польше</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8933">Poland tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8934">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8934">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8935">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8935">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8936">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8936">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8937">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8937">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8938">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8938">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8939">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8939">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8940">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8940">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8941">11 цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8941">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8942">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8942">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8943">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8943">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8944">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8944">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8945">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8945">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8946">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8946">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8947">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8947">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8948">Функция находит  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8948">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8949">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8949">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
  
```xml
      <!-- Poland Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="1ff28b4d-40f2-49e9-b677-9606a88e2bca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-citizen-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8979">Номер карточки гражданина Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8979">Portugal citizen card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8980">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8980">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8981">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8981">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8982">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8982">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8983">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8983">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8984">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8984">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8985">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8985">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8986">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8986">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8987">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8987">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8988">регулярное выражение Regex_portugal_citizen_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8988">The regular expression Regex_portugal_citizen_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-8989">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_portugal_citizen_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-8989">A keyword from Keyword_portugal_citizen_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Portugal Citizen Card Number -->
<Entity id="91a7ece2-add4-4986-9a15-c84544d81ecd" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_citizen_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_portugal_citizen_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9009">Номер водительских прав Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9009">Portugal driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9010">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9010">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9011">два шаблона : две буквы с 5-8 цифрами со специальными символами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9011">two patterns - two letters followed by 5-8 digits with special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9012">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9012">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9013">Шаблон 1. Две буквы, за которыми следуют 5/6 со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9013">Pattern 1: Two letters followed by 5/6 with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9014">Две буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9014">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9015">дефис;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9015">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9016">Пять или шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9016">Five or Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9017">Пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9017">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9018">Одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9018">One digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9019">Шаблон 2. Одна буква с 6/8 цифрами со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9019">Pattern 2: One letter followed by 6/8 digits with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9020">Одна буква (не деликатная)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9020">One letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9021">дефис;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9021">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9022">Шесть или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9022">Six or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9023">Пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9023">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9024">одна цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9024">One digit</span></span>

    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9025">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9025">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9026">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9026">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9027">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9027">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9028">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9028">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9029">Обычное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9029">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9030">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9030">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="977f1e5a-2c33-4bcc-b516-95bb275cff23" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9162">Номер паспорта Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9162">Portugal passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9163">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9163">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9164">одна буква с шестью цифрами без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9164">one letter followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9165">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9165">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9166">одна буква с шестью цифрами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9166">one letter followed by six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9167">одна буква (не деликатная)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9167">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9168">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9168">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9169">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9169">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9170">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9170">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9171">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9171">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9172">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9172">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9173">Обычное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9173">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9174">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9174">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9175">Обычное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате DD.MM.YYYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9175">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9176">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9176">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9177">Обычное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9177">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9178">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9178">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="080a52fd-a7bc-431e-b54d-51f08f59db11" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9205">Идентификация налога в Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9205">Portugal tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9206">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9206">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9207">девять цифр с необязательными пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9207">nine digits with optional spaces</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9208">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9208">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9209">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9209">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9210">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9210">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9211">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9211">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9212">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9212">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9213">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9213">three digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9214">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9214">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9215">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9215">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9216">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9216">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9217">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9217">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9218">Функция находит  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9218">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9219">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9219">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9220">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9220">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9221">Функция находит  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9221">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="65372402-3131-4f1e-9983-4439841d1f15" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9246">Номер лицензии водителя в Румынии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9246">Romania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9247">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9247">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9248">один символ с восемью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9248">one character followed by eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9249">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9249">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9250">один символ с восемью цифрами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9250">one character followed by eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9251">одна буква (не чувствительная к делу) или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9251">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9252">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9252">eight digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9253">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9253">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9254">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9254">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9255">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9255">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9256">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9256">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9257">Обычное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9257">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9258">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9258">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="b5511ace-2fd8-4ae4-b6fc-c7c6e4689e3c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-personal-numeric-code-cnp"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9386">Личный числимый код Румынии (CNP)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9386">Romania personal numeric code (CNP)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9387">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9387">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9388">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9388">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9389">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9389">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9390">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9390">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9391">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9391">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9392">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9392">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9393">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9393">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9394">13 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9394">13 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9395">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9395">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9396">одна цифра из 1-9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9396">one digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9397">шесть цифр, представляющих дату рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9397">six digits representing date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9398">две цифры, которые могут быть 01-52 или 99</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9398">two digits, which can be 01-52 or 99</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9399">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9399">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9400">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9400">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9401">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9401">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9402">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9402">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9403">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9403">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9404">Функция находит  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9404">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9405">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9405">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9406">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9406">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9407">Функция находит  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9407">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Personal Numerical Code (CNP) -->
      <Entity id="eb5fa399-fe28-4c67-8188-d63a616ed89c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9458">Номер паспорта Румынии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9458">Romania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9459">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9459">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9460">восемь или девять цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9460">eight or nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9461">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9461">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9462">восемь или девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9462">eight or nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9463">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9463">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9464">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9464">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9465">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9465">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9466">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9466">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9467">Обычное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9467">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9468">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9468">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9469">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_romania_eu_passport_date` DD MMM/MMM YY (Пример- 01 FEB/FEB 10) или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9469">The regular expression `Regex_romania_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YY (Example- 01 FEB/FEB 10) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9470">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9470">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9471">Обычное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9471">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9472">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9472">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="5d31b90c-7fe2-4a76-a14b-767b8fd19d6c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9478">паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9478">passports</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9483">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9483">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9484">номера паспортов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9484">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_romania_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9485">Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9485">Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number</span></span>
