## <a name="russia-passport-number-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9490">Номер паспорта России внутренний</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9490">Russia passport number domestic</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9491">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9491">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9492">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9492">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9493">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9493">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9494">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9494">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9495">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9495">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9496">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9496">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9497">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9497">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9498">10-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9498">10-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9499">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9499">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9500">10-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9500">10-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9501">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9501">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9502">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9502">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9503">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9503">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9504">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9504">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9505">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9505">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9506">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9506">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9507">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9507">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9508">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9508">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9509">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9509">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9510">В regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9510">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9511">Ключевое слово Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9511">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number Domestic -->
      <Entity id="76ec2f5d-cedb-48e1-8070-1998794af445" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9514">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9514">passport number</span></span>

## <a name="russia-passport-number-international"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9528">Номер паспорта России</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9528">Russia passport number international</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9529">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9529">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9535">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9535">Format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9537">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9537">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9538">девятизначный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9538">nine-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9541">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9541">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9542">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9542">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9543">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9543">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9544">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9544">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9545">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9545">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9546">В regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9546">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9547">Ключевое слово Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9547">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number International -->
      <Entity id="ac5f4878-75e4-4b82-af2d-02e13ea9f411" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="saudi-arabia-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9564">Национальный идентификатор для Саудовской Аравии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9564">Saudi Arabia National ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9565">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9565">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9566">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9566">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9567">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9567">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9568">10 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9568">10 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9569">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9569">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9570">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9570">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9571">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9571">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9572">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9572">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9573">регулярное выражение Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9573">The regular expression Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9574">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9574">A keyword from Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Saudi Arabia National ID -->
<Entity id="8c5a0ba8-404a-41a3-8871-746aa21ee6c0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9575">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9575">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9576">Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9576">Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9577">Identification Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9577">Identification Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9578">I card number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9578">I card number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9579">ID number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9579">ID number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9580">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9580">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span></span> 

   
## <a name="singapore-national-registration-identity-card-nric-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9581">Номер удостоверения удостоверения национальной регистрации Сингапура (NRIC)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9581">Singapore national registration identity card (NRIC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9582">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9582">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9583">девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9583">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9584">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9584">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9585">девять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9585">nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9586">буквы "F", "G", "S" или "T" (не чувствительны к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9586">the letter "F", "G", "S", or "T" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9587">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9587">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9588">цифру проверки алфавита</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9588">an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9589">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9589">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9590">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9590">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9591">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9591">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9592">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9592">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9593">регулярное выражение Regex_singapore_nric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9593">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9594">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_singapore_nric;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9594">A keyword from Keyword_singapore_nric is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9595">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9595">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9596">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9596">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9597">регулярное выражение Regex_singapore_nric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9597">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9598">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9598">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Singapore National Registration Identity Card (NRIC) Number -->
<Entity id="cead390a-dd83-4856-9751-fb6dc98c34da" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9599">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9599">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9608">身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9608">身份證</span></span> 

## <a name="slovakia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9609">Номер лицензии водителя Словакии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9609">Slovakia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9610">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9610">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9611">один символ, за которым следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9611">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9612">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9612">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9613">один символ, за которым следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9613">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9614">одна буква (не чувствительная к делу) или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9614">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9615">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9615">seven digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9616">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9616">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9617">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9617">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9618">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9618">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9619">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9619">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9620">Обычное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9620">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9621">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9621">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="14240c22-b6de-4ce5-a90b-137f74252513" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovakia-personal-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9747">Личный номер Словакии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9747">Slovakia personal number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9748">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9748">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9749">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9749">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9750">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9750">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9751">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9751">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9752">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9752">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9753">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9753">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9754">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9754">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9755">9 или 10 цифр, содержащих необязательный ответный ответ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9755">nine or 10 digits containing optional backslash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9756">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9756">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9757">шесть цифр, представляющих дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9757">six digits representing date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9758">необязательный слэш (/)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9758">optional slash (/)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9759">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9759">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9760">одна необязательная цифра проверки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9760">one optional check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9761">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9761">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9762">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9762">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9763">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9763">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9764">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9764">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9765">Функция находит  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9765">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9766">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9766">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9767">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9767">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9768">Функция находит  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9768">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Personal Number -->
      <Entity id="951c26b7-3b35-4f73-924b-15dd599cb9ab" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

## <a name="slovakia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9815">Номер паспорта Словакии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9815">Slovakia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9816">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9816">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9817">одна цифра или буква, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9817">one digit or letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9818">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9818">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9819">одна цифра или буква (не чувствительные к делу) с последующим семизначным числом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9819">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9820">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9820">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9821">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9821">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9822">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9822">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9823">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9823">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9824">Обычное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9824">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9825">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9825">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9826">Обычное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате DD.MM.YYYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9826">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9827">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9827">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9828">Обычное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9828">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9829">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9829">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="238e1f08-d80e-4793-af33-9b57918335b7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9842">Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9842">Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

## <a name="slovenia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9851">Номер лицензии водителя Словении</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9851">Slovenia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9852">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9852">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9853">девять цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9853">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9854">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9854">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9855">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9855">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9856">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9856">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9857">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9857">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9858">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9858">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9859">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9859">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9860">Обычное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9860">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9861">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9861">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5bc089a-f2ee-433d-a6b1-5c253051d6f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9991">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9991">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9992">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9992">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9993">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9993">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9994">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9994">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9995">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9995">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9996">13 цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9996">13 digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9997">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9997">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9998">13 цифр в указанном шаблоне:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9998">13 digits in the specified pattern:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-9999">семь цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (DDMMLLL), где "LLL" соответствует последним трем цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-9999">seven digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMLLL) where "LLL" corresponds to the last three digits of the birth year</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10000">две цифры, соответствующие области рождения "50"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10000">two digits that correspond to the area of birth "50"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10001">три цифры, соответствующие сочетанию пола и серийного номера для лиц, родившихся в один день.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10001">three digits that correspond to a combination of gender and serial number for persons born on the same day.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10002">000-499 для мужчин и 500-999 для женщин.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10002">000-499 for male and 500-999 for female.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10003">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10003">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10004">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10004">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10005">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10005">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10006">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10006">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10007">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10007">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10008">Функция находит  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10008">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10009">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10009">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10010">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10010">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10011">Функция находит  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10011">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number -->
      <Entity id="68948b27-803d-41e4-adf1-13e05eb541bb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10039">Номер паспорта Словении</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10039">Slovenia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10040">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10040">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10041">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10041">two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10042">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10042">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10043">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10043">two letters followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10044">буква "P"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10044">the letter "P"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10045">одно верхнее письмо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10045">one uppercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10046">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10046">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10047">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10047">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10048">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10048">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10049">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10049">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10050">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10050">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10051">Обычное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10051">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10052">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10052">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10053">Обычное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате DD.MM.YYYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10053">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10054">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10054">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10055">Обычное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10055">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10056">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10056">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="235b7976-7bbe-4df5-bb40-08678e749d1a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10058">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10058">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10066">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10066">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10067">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10067">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10068">номера паспортов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10068">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10069">Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10069">Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10070">številka potnega lista</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10070">številka potnega lista</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10071">potek veljavnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10071">potek veljavnosti</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10072">список potni #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10072">potni list#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10073">datum rojstva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10073">datum rojstva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10074">список potni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10074">potni list</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10075">številke potnih listov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10075">številke potnih listov</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10077">дата выпуска</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10077">date of issue</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10078">дата истечения срока действия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10078">date of expiry</span></span>


## <a name="slovenia-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10079">Идентификационный номер налога в Словении</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10079">Slovenia tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10080">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10080">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10081">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10081">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10082">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10082">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10083">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10083">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10084">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10084">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10085">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10085">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10086">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10086">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10087">восемь цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10087">eight digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10088">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10088">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10089">одна цифра из 1-9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10089">one digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10090">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10090">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10091">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10091">one check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10092">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10092">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10093">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10093">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10094">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10094">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10095">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10095">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10096">Функция находит  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10096">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10097">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10097">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10098">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10098">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10099">Функция находит  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10099">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="e47b071e-c352-4d70-8241-8c215ad65505" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10103">identifikacijska številka davka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10103">identifikacijska številka davka</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10104">številka davčne datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10104">številka davčne datoteke</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10110">нет налога #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10110">tax no#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10112">налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10112">tax number</span></span>

## <a name="south-africa-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10123">Идентификационный номер Южной Африки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10123">South Africa identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10124">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10124">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10125">13 цифр, которые могут содержать пробелы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10125">13 digits that may contain spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10126">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10126">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10127">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10127">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10128">шесть цифр в формате YYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10128">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10129">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10129">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10130">однозначный индикатор гражданства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10130">a single-digit citizenship indicator</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10131">цифры "8" или "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10131">the digit "8" or "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10132">одна цифра, которая является цифрой чека</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10132">one digit, which is a checksum digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10133">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10133">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10134">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10134">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10135">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10135">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10136">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10136">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10137">функция Func_south_africa_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10137">The function Func_south_africa_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10138">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_south_africa_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10138">A keyword from Keyword_south_africa_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10139">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10139">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Africa Identification Number -->
<Entity id="e2adf7cb-8ea6-4048-a2ed-d89eb65f2780" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_africa_identification_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_africa_identification_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10140">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10140">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_south_africa_identification_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10141">Keyword_south_africa_identification_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10141">Keyword_south_africa_identification_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10142">Identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10142">Identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10143">ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10143">ID</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10144">Идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10144">Identification</span></span> 
   
## <a name="south-korea-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10145">Номер регистрации резидента Южной Кореи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10145">South Korea resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10146">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10146">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10147">13 цифр, содержащих дефис.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10147">13 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10148">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10148">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10149">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10149">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10150">шесть цифр в формате YYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10150">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10151">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10151">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10152">одна цифра, определяемая веком и полом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10152">one digit determined by the century and gender</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10153">четырехзначный код региона рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10153">four-digit region-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10154">одна цифра, используемая для дифференцировки людей, для которых предыдущие номера идентичны</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10154">one digit used to differentiate people for whom the preceding numbers are identical</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10155">контрольная цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10155">a check digit.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10156">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10156">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10157">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10157">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10158">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10158">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10159">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10159">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10160">функция Func_south_korea_resident_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10160">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10161">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_south_korea_resident_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10161">A keyword from Keyword_south_korea_resident_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10162">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10162">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10163">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10163">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10164">функция Func_south_korea_resident_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10164">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10165">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10165">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Korea Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="5b802e18-ba80-44c4-bc83-bf2ad36ae36a" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10166">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10166">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_south_korea_resident_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10167">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10167">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10168">National ID card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10168">National ID card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10169">Citizen's Registration Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10169">Citizen's Registration Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10170">Jumin deungnok beonho</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10170">Jumin deungnok beonho</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10171">RRN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10171">RRN</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10172">주민등록번호</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10172">주민등록번호</span></span>

## <a name="spain-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10173">Номер водительских прав Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10173">Spain driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10174">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10174">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10175">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10175">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10176">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10176">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10177">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10177">eight digits followed by one character:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10178">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10178">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10179">одна цифра или буква (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10179">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10180">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10180">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10181">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10181">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10182">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10182">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10183">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10183">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10184">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` поиск контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10184">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10185">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10185">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10186">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10186">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10187">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` поиск контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10187">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5a82922-b501-4f40-8868-341321146aa2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-dni"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10321">DNI Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10321">Spain DNI</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10322">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10322">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10323">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10323">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10324">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10324">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10325">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10325">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10326">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10326">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10327">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10327">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10328">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10328">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10329">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10329">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10330">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10330">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10331">семь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10331">seven digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10332">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10332">eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10333">Необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10333">An optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10334">одно чековая буква (не чувствительное к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10334">one check letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10335">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10335">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10336">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10336">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10337">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10337">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10338">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10338">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10339">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` поиск контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10339">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10340">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10340">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10341">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10341">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10342">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` поиск контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10342">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

    
```xml
      <!-- Spain DNI -->
      <Entity id="8e6251b9-47b4-40e8-a42b-0f80876be192" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10366">Номер паспорта Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10366">Spain passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10367">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10367">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10368">сочетание букв и номеров с восемью или девятью символами без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10368">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10369">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10369">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10370">сочетание букв и номеров с восемью или девятью символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10370">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10371">две цифры или буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10371">two digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10372">одна цифра или буква (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10372">one digit or letter (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10373">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10373">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10374">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10374">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10375">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10375">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10376">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10376">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10377">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10377">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10378">Обычное выражение  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10378">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10379">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10379">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10380">Регулярное выражение `Regex_spain_eu_passport_date` находит дату в формате DD-MM-YYYYY или найдено ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10380">The regular expression `Regex_spain_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD-MM-YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10381">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10381">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10382">Обычное выражение  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10382">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10383">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10383">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d17a57de-9fa5-4e9f-85d3-85c26d89686e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_spain_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10396">Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10396">Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10397">libreta pasaporte</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10397">libreta pasaporte</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10399">españa pasaporte</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10399">españa pasaporte</span></span>

## <a name="spain-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10412">Номер социального обеспечения Испании (SSN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10412">Spain social security number (SSN)</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10413">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10413">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10414">11–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10414">11-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10415">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10415">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10416">11-12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10416">11-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10417">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10417">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10418">косая черта (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10418">a forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10419">семь-восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10419">seven to eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10420">косая черта (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10420">a forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10421">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10421">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10422">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10422">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10423">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10423">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10424">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10424">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10425">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10425">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10426">функция Func_spanish_social_security_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10426">The function Func_spanish_social_security_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10427">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10427">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10428">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10428">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10429">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10429">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10430">функция Func_spanish_social_security_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10430">The function Func_spanish_social_security_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10431">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10431">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- Spain SSN -->
    <Entity id="5df987c0-8eae-4bce-ace7-b316347f3070" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85" relaxProximity="true" >
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spanish_social_security_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spanish_social_security_number" />
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```
