#### <a name="keywords_spain_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10433">Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10433">Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10434">ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10434">ssn</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10436">socialsecurityno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10436">socialsecurityno</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10437">социального обеспечения нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10437">social security no</span></span>

## <a name="spain-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10440">Идентификация налога в Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10440">Spain tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10441">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10441">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10442">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10442">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10443">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10443">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10444">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10444">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10445">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10445">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10446">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10446">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10447">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10447">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10448">семь или восемь цифр и одна или две буквы в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10448">seven or eight digits and one or two letters in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10449">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10449">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10450">Испанские граждане с национальным удостоверением личности Испании:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10450">Spanish Natural Persons with a Spain National Identity Card:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10451">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10451">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10452">одно верхнее письмо (чувствительный к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10452">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10453">Испанцы-нерезиденты без национального удостоверения личности Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10453">Non-resident Spaniards without a Spain National Identity Card</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10454">одно верхнее письмо "L" (чувствительный к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10454">one uppercase letter "L" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10455">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10455">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10456">одно верхнее письмо (чувствительный к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10456">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10457">Resident Spaniards under the age of 14 years without a Spain National Identity Card:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10457">Resident Spaniards under the age of 14 years without a Spain National Identity Card:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10458">одно верхнее письмо "K" (чувствительный к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10458">one uppercase letter "K" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10459">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10459">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10460">одно верхнее письмо (чувствительный к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10460">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10461">Иностранцы с идентификационным номером иностранца</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10461">Foreigners with a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10462">одно верхнее письмо с буквами "X", "Y" или "Z" (чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10462">one uppercase letter that is "X", "Y", or "Z" (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10463">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10463">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10464">одно верхнее письмо (чувствительный к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10464">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10465">Иностранцы без идентификации иностранца</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10465">Foreigners without a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10466">одно верхнее письмо с буквой "M" (чувствительный к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10466">one uppercase letter that is "M" (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10467">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10467">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10468">одно верхнее письмо (чувствительный к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10468">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10469">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10469">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10470">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10470">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10471">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10471">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10472">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10472">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10473">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` поиск контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10473">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10474">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10474">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10475">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10475">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10476">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` поиск контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10476">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="10f0d113-b0e1-47dc-872a-a4f45b9376a3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sql-server-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10507">SQL Server подключения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10507">SQL Server connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10508">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10508">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10509">Строка "User Id", "User ID", "uid" или "UserId" с символами и строками, описанными в приведенной ниже схеме.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10509">The string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10510">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10510">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10511">строки "User Id", "User ID", "uid" или "UserId"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10511">the string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10512">любое сочетание между 1-200 буквами нижнего или верхнего шкафа, цифрами, символами, специальными символами или пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10512">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10513">строка "Пароль" или "pwd", где "pwd" не предшествует букве нижнего регистра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10513">the string "Password" or "pwd" where "pwd" isn't preceded by a lowercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10514">равный знак (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10514">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10515">любой символ, который не является символом доллара ($), процентным символом (%), больше символа (>), в символе (@), кавычках ("), зайколоне (;), левом скобке ([) или левой скобке ({)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10515">any character that isn't a dollar sign ($), percent symbol (%), greater than symbol (>), at symbol (@), quotation mark ("), semicolon (;), left brace([), or left bracket ({)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10516">любое сочетание из 7-128 символов, которые не являются полуколоном (;), слэшом (/) или кавычками ()</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10516">any combination of 7-128 characters that are not a semicolon (;), forward slash (/), or quotation mark (")</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10517">полуколон (;) или кавычка ()</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10517">a semicolon (;) or quotation mark (")</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10518">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10518">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10519">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10519">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10520">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10520">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10521">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10521">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10522">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10522">The regular expression CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10523">Ключевое слово CEP_GlobalFilter не найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10523">A keyword from CEP_GlobalFilter isn't found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10524">Обычное выражение CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder не находит контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10524">The regular expression CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10525">Обычное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10525">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```sql
<!---SQL Server Connection String>
<Entity id="e76b6205-d3cb-46f2-bd63-c90153f2f97d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_GlobalFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10526">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10526">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_globalfilter"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10527">CEP_GlobalFilter</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10527">CEP_GlobalFilter</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10528">some-password</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10528">some-password</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10529">somepassword</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10529">somepassword</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10530">secretPassword</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10530">secretPassword</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10531">пример</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10531">sample</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_passwordplaceholder"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10532">CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10532">CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10533">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации определяет эти ключевые слова с помощью регулярного выражения, а не списка ключевых слов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10533">This sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10534">Пароль или pwd с 0-2 пробелами, равным знаком (=), пробелами 0-2 и звездочкой (\*) -OR-</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10534">Password or pwd followed by 0-2 spaces, an equal sign (=), 0-2 spaces, and an asterisk (\*) -OR-</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10535">Пароль или pwd, за которыми следуют:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10535">Password or pwd followed by:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10536">Равный знак (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10536">Equal sign (=)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10537">Меньше символа (<)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10537">Less than symbol (<)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10538">Любое сочетание 1-200 символов, которые являются буквами верхнего или нижнего регистра, цифрами, звездочкой (\*), дефисом (-), подчеркнув (_) или символом whitespace</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10538">Any combination of 1-200 characters that are upper- or lowercase letters, digits, an asterisk (\*), hyphen (-), underline (_), or whitespace character</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10539">Больше символа (>)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10539">Greater than symbol (>)</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_commonexamplekeywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10540">CEP_CommonExampleKeywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10540">CEP_CommonExampleKeywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10541">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации определяет эти ключевые слова с помощью регулярного выражения, а не списка ключевых слов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10541">This sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10549">тесты.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10549">testacs.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10550">com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10550">com</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10551">s-int.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10551">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10552">net</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10552">net</span></span>

## <a name="sweden-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10553">Номер водительских прав Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10553">Sweden driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10554">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10554">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10555">10 цифр, содержащих дефис.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10555">10 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10556">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10556">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10557">10 цифр, содержащих дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10557">10 digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10558">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10558">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10559">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10559">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10560">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10560">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10561">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10561">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10562">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10562">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10563">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10563">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10564">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10564">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10565">Обычное выражение  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10565">The regular expression  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10566">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10566">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="70088720-90dd-47f5-805e-5525f3567391" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10699">Национальный ID Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10699">Sweden national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10700">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10700">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10701">10 или 12 цифр и дополнительный разделитель.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10701">10 or 12 digits and an optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10702">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10702">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10703">10 или 12 цифр с необязательным разделителем</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10703">10 or 12 digits and an optional delimiter:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10704">две цифры (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10704">two digits (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10705">Шесть цифр в формате даты ГГММДД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10705">Six digits in date format YYMMDD</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10706">delimiter из "-" или "+" (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10706">delimiter of "-" or "+" (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10707">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10707">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10708">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10708">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10709">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10709">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10710">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10710">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10711">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10711">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10712">Функция находит `Func_swedish_national_identifier` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10712">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10713">Найдено `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` ключевое слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10713">A keyword from `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10714">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10714">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10715">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10715">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10716">Функция находит `Func_swedish_national_identifier` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10716">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10717">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10717">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- Sweden National ID -->
    <Entity id="f69aaf40-79be-4fac-8f05-fd1910d272c8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10718">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10718">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="sweden-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10736">Номер паспорта Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10736">Sweden passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10737">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10737">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10738">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10738">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10739">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10739">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10740">восемь последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10740">eight consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10741">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10741">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10742">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10742">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10743">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10743">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10744">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10744">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10745">регулярное выражение Regex_sweden_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10745">the regular expression Regex_sweden_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10746">ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` или `Keyword_sweden_passport` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10746">a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_sweden_passport` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10747">обычное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date` DD MMM/MMM YY (01 JAN/JAN 12) или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из найденного.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10747">the regular expression `Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date` finds a date in the format DD MMM/MMM YY (01 JAN/JAN 12) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10748">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10748">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10749">регулярное выражение Regex_sweden_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10749">the regular expression Regex_sweden_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10750">ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` или `Keyword_sweden_passport` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10750">a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_sweden_passport` is found.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- Sweden Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="ba4e7456-55a9-4d89-9140-c33673553526" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_sweden_passport" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_sweden_passport" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10786">Номер налоговой идентификации в Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10786">Sweden tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10787">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10787">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10788">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10788">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10789">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10789">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10790">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10790">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10791">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10791">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10792">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10792">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10793">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10793">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10794">10 цифр и символ в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10794">10 digits and a symbol in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10795">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10795">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10796">10 цифр и символ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10796">10 digits and a symbol:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10797">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10797">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10798">знак плюс или минус</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10798">a plus sign or minus sign</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10799">три цифры, которые делают идентификационный номер уникальным, где:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10799">three digits that make the identification number unique where:</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10800">для номеров, выдавшихся до 1990 г., седьмая и восьмая цифры определяют округ родившихся или родившихся за</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10800">for numbers issued before 1990, the seventh and eighth digit identify the county of birth or foreign-born people</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10801">цифра в девятой позиции указывает пол по нечетным для мужчин или даже для женщин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10801">the digit in the ninth position indicates gender by either odd for male or even for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10802">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10802">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10803">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10803">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10804">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10804">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10805">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10805">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10806">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10806">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10807">Функция находит  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10807">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10808">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10808">A keyword from  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10809">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10809">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10810">Функция находит  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10810">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="139acba0-a5bc-4fbb-876d-f7a493ae8a40" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10811">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10811">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10812">Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10812">Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10813">личный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10813">personal id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10814">personnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10814">personnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10815">кадетский id nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10815">skatt id nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10816">идентификация фигурного катания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10816">skatt identifikation</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10817">skattebetalarens identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10817">skattebetalarens identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10818">sverige tin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10818">sverige tin</span></span>

## <a name="swift-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10836">Код SWIFT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10836">SWIFT code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10837">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10837">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10838">четыре буквы с последующим 5-31 буквами или цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10838">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10839">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10839">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10840">четыре буквы, за которыми следуют 5-31 буквы или цифры:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10840">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10841">банковский код с четырьмя буквами (не чувствительный к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10841">four-letter bank code (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10842">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10842">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10843">4–28 букв или цифр (основной номер банковского счета, BBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10843">4-28 letters or digits (the Basic Bank Account Number (BBAN))</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10844">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10844">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10845">от одной до трех букв или цифр (остальная часть BBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10845">one to three letters or digits (remainder of the BBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10846">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10846">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10847">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10847">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10848">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10848">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10849">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10849">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10850">регулярное выражение Regex_swift находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10850">The regular expression Regex_swift finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10851">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_swift.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10851">A keyword from Keyword_swift is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="cb2ab58c-9cb8-4c81-baf8-a4e106791df4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_swift" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_swift" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="switzerland-ssn-ahv-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10888">Номер AHV SSN в Швейцарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10888">Switzerland SSN AHV number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10889">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10889">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10890">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10890">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10891">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10891">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10892">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10892">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10893">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10893">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10894">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10894">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10895">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10895">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10896">13-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10896">13-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10897">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10897">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10898">13-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10898">13-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10899">три цифры - 756</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10899">three digits - 756</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10900">необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10900">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10901">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10901">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10902">необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10902">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10903">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10903">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10904">необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10904">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10905">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10905">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10906">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10906">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10907">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10907">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10908">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10908">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10909">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10909">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10910">Функция Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10910">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10911">Ключевое слово Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10911">A keyword from Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10912">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10912">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10913">Функция Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10913">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Swiss SSN AHV Number -->
      <Entity id="277cfa4b-6eaa-4a1b-9492-099dec849971" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10931">sozialversicherungsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10931">sozialversicherungsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10932">идентификационный код personnelle</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10932">identification personnelle id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10933">numéro de sécurité sociale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10933">numéro de sécurité sociale</span></span>

   
## <a name="taiwan-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10934">Национальный идентификационный номер Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10934">Taiwan national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10935">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10935">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10936">одна буква (на английском языке) с девятью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10936">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10937">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10937">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10938">одна буква (на английском языке), а затем девять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10938">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10939">одна буква (на английском языке, а не на английском языке)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10939">one letter (in English, not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10940">цифры "1" или "2"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10940">the digit "1" or "2"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10941">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10941">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10942">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10942">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10943">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10943">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10944">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10944">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10945">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10945">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10946">функция Func_taiwanese_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10946">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10947">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwanese_national_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10947">A keyword from Keyword_taiwanese_national_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10948">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10948">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10949">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10949">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10950">функция Func_taiwanese_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10950">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10951">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10951">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwanese National ID -->
<Entity id="4C7BFC34-8DD1-421D-8FB7-6C6182C2AF03" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwanese_national_id" />
      </Pattern>
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
         <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
       </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10952">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10952">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10953">Keyword_taiwan_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10953">Keyword_taiwan_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10954">身份證字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10954">身份證字號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10955">身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10955">身份證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10956">身份證號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10956">身份證號碼</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10957">身份證號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10957">身份證號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10958">身分證字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10958">身分證字號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10959">身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10959">身分證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10960">身分證號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10960">身分證號碼</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10961">身份證號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10961">身份證號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10962">身分證統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10962">身分證統一編號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10963">國民身分證統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10963">國民身分證統一編號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10964">簽名</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10964">簽名</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10965">蓋章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10965">蓋章</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10966">簽名或蓋章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10966">簽名或蓋章</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10967">簽章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10967">簽章</span></span>   
   
## <a name="taiwan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10968">Номер паспорта Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10968">Taiwan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10969">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10969">Format</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10970">биометрический номер паспорта: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10970">biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10971">не биометрический номер паспорта: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10971">non-biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10972">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10972">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10973">биометрический номер паспорта:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10973">biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10974">символ "3"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10974">the character "3"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10975">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10975">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10976">не биометрический номер паспорта:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10976">non-biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10977">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10977">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10978">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10978">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10979">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10979">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10980">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10980">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10981">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10981">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10982">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10982">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10983">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10983">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="e7251cb4-4c2c-41df-963e-924eb3dae04a" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_passport"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_passport"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10984">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10984">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10985">Keyword_taiwan_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10985">Keyword_taiwan_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10986">ROC passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10986">ROC passport number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10987">Passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10987">Passport number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10988">Passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10988">Passport no</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10989">Passport Num</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10989">Passport Num</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10990">Passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10990">Passport #</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10991">护照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10991">护照</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10992">中華民國護照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10992">中華民國護照</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10993">Zhōnghuá Mínguó hùzhào</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10993">Zhōnghuá Mínguó hùzhào</span></span>
   
## <a name="taiwan-resident-certificate-arctarc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10994">Номер сертификата жителя Тайваня (ARC/TARC)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10994">Taiwan-resident certificate (ARC/TARC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10995">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10995">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10996">10 букв и цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10996">10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10997">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10997">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10998">10 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10998">10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-10999">две буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-10999">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11000">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11000">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11001">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11001">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11002">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11002">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11003">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11003">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11004">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11004">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11005">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11005">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11006">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11006">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Resident Certificate (ARC/TARC) -->
<Entity id="48269fec-05ea-46ea-b326-f5623a58c6e9" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11007">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11007">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11008">Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11008">Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11009">Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11009">Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11010">Resident Cert</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11010">Resident Cert</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11011">Resident Cert.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11011">Resident Cert.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11012">Identification card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11012">Identification card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11013">Alien Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11013">Alien Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11014">ARC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11014">ARC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11015">Taiwan Area Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11015">Taiwan Area Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11016">TARC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11016">TARC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11017">居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11017">居留證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11018">外僑居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11018">外僑居留證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11019">台灣地區居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11019">台灣地區居留證</span></span> 

## <a name="thai-population-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11020">Код идентификации населения Таиланда</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11020">Thai population identification code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11021">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11021">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11022">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11022">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11023">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11023">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11024">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11024">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11025">первая цифра не ноль или девять</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11025">first digit isn't zero or nine</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11026">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11026">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11027">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11027">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11028">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11028">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11029">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11029">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11030">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11030">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11031">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11031">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11032">Ключевое слово Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11032">A keyword from Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11033">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11033">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11034">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11034">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Thai Citizen ID -->
-<Entity id="44ca9e86-ead7-4c5d-884a-e2eaa401515e" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="turkish-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11043">Турецкий национальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11043">Turkish national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11044">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11044">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11045">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11045">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11046">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11046">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11047">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11047">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11048">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11048">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11049">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11049">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11050">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11050">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11051">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11051">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11052">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11052">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11053">Ключевое слово из Keyword_Turkish_National_Id найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11053">A keyword from Keyword_Turkish_National_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11054">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11054">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11055">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11055">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Turkish National Identity -->
-<Entity id="fb621f20-3876-4cfc-acec-8c8e73ca32c7" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11056">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11056">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_turkish_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11057">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11057">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11058">TC Kimlik No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11058">TC Kimlik No</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11061">Vatandaşlık нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11061">Vatandaşlık no</span></span>

## <a name="uk-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11062">U.K.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11062">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11063">номер лицензии водителя</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11063">driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11064">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11064">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11065">Сочетание 18 букв и цифр в указанном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11065">Combination of 18 letters and digits in the specified format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11066">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11066">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11067">18 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11067">18 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11068">Пять букв (не чувствительных к делу) или цифра "9" на месте буквы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11068">Five letters (not case-sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11069">Одна цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11069">One digit.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11070">Пять цифр в формате даты MMDDY для даты рождения.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11070">Five digits in the date format MMDDY for date of birth.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11071">Седьмой символ приумножен на 50, если драйвер женский; для экзамена, от 51 до 62 вместо 01 до 12.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11071">The seventh character is incremented by 50 if driver is female; for exampe, 51 to 62 instead of 01 to 12.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11072">Две буквы (не чувствительные к делу) или цифра "9" на месте буквы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11072">Two letters (not case-sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11073">Пять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11073">Five digits.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11074">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11074">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11075">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11075">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11076">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11076">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11077">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11077">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11078">Функция находит `Func_uk_drivers_license` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11078">The function `Func_uk_drivers_license` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11079">Найдено ключевое `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11079">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11080">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11080">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11081">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11081">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11082">Функция находит `Func_uk_drivers_license` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11082">The function `Func_uk_drivers_license` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11083">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11083">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.K. Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="f93de4be-d94c-40df-a8be-461738047551" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true" >
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```
