## <a name="uk-electoral-roll-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11204">U.K.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11204">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11205">номер списка выборов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11205">electoral roll number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11206">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11206">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11207">две буквы, за которыми следуют 1-4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11207">two letters followed by 1-4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11208">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11208">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11209">две буквы (не чувствительные к делу) с последующим 1-4 числами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11209">two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by 1-4 numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11210">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11210">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11211">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11211">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11212">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11212">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11213">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11213">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11214">регулярное выражение Regex_uk_electoral находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11214">The regular expression Regex_uk_electoral finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11215">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_electoral.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11215">A keyword from Keyword_uk_electoral is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Electoral Number -->
<Entity id="a3eea206-dc0c-4f06-9e22-aa1be3059963" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_uk_electoral" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_electoral" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11216">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11216">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_electoral"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11217">Keyword_uk_electoral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11217">Keyword_uk_electoral</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11218">council nomination</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11218">council nomination</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11219">nomination form</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11219">nomination form</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11220">electoral register</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11220">electoral register</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11221">electoral roll</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11221">electoral roll</span></span>

   
## <a name="uk-national-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11222">U.K.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11222">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11223">номер службы здравоохранения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11223">national health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11224">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11224">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11225">10–17 цифр, разделенных пробелами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11225">10-17 digits separated by spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11226">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11226">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11227">10-17 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11227">10-17 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11228">3 или 10 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11228">either 3 or 10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11229">пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11229">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11230">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11230">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11231">пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11231">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11232">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11232">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11233">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11233">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11234">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11234">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11235">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11235">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11236">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11236">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11237">Функция Func_uk_nhs_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11237">The function Func_uk_nhs_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11238">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11238">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11239">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11239">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11240">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number1;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11240">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11241">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11241">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11242">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11242">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. NHS Number -->
<Entity id="3192014e-2a16-44e9-aa69-4b20375c9a78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nhs_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11243">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11243">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11244">Keyword_uk_nhs_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11244">Keyword_uk_nhs_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11245">national health service</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11245">national health service</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11246">NHS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11246">nhs</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11247">health services authority</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11247">health services authority</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11248">health authority</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11248">health authority</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number1"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11249">Keyword_uk_nhs_number1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11249">Keyword_uk_nhs_number1</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11250">patient id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11250">patient id</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11251">patient identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11251">patient identification</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11252">patient no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11252">patient no</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11253">patient number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11253">patient number</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11254">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11254">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11255">GP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11255">GP</span></span>

## <a name="uk-national-insurance-number-nino"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11260">U.K.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11260">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11261">номер национального страхования (NINO)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11261">national insurance number (NINO)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11262">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации входит в тип конфиденциальной информации о номере национальной идентификации ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11262">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11263">Он также доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11263">It's also available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11264">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11264">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11265">семь символов или девять символов, разделенных пробелами или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11265">seven characters or nine characters separated by spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11266">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11266">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11267">два возможных шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11267">two possible patterns:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11268">две буквы (допустимые ННИ используют только определенные символы в этом префиксе, который этот шаблон проверяет; не является чувствительным к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11268">two letters (valid NINOs use only certain characters in this prefix, which this pattern validates; not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11269">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11269">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11270">или "A", "B", "C", "D" (как и префикс, в суффиксе разрешены только определенные символы, не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11270">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D' (like the prefix, only certain characters are allowed in the suffix; not case-sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11271">ИЛИ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11271">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11272">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11272">two letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11273">пространство или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11273">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11274">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11274">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11275">пространство или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11275">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11276">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11276">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11277">пространство или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11277">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11278">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11278">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11279">пространство или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11279">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11280">"A", "B", "C" или "D"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11280">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D'</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11281">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11281">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11282">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11282">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11283">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11283">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11284">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11284">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11285">функция Func_uk_nino находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11285">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11286">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11286">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nino is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11287">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11287">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11288">функция Func_uk_nino находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11288">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.K. NINO -->
    <Entity id="16c07343-c26f-49d2-a987-3daf717e94cc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-unique-taxpayer-reference-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11310">U.K.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11310">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11311">Уникальный номер ссылки на налогоплательщика</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11311">Unique Taxpayer Reference Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11312">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11312">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11313">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11313">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11314">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11314">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11315">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11315">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11316">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11316">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11317">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11317">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11318">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11318">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11319">10 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11319">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
 
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11320">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11320">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11321">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11321">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11322">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11322">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11323">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11323">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11324">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11324">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11325">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11325">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11326">Функция находит  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11326">The function  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11327">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11327">A keyword from  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- U.K. Unique Taxpayer Reference Number -->
      <Entity id="ad4a8116-0db8-439a-b545-6d967642f0ec" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11336">нет налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11336">tax no</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11338">таксомоторный #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11338">taxid#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11345">олово нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11345">tin no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11346">олово #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11346">tin#</span></span>

## <a name="us-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11347">Номер банковского счета в США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11347">U.S. bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11348">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11348">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11349">6-17 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11349">6-17 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11350">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11350">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11351">6-17 последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11351">6-17 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11352">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11352">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11353">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11353">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11354">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11354">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11355">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11355">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11356">регулярное выражение Regex_usa_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11356">The regular expression Regex_usa_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11357">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_usa_Bank_Account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11357">A keyword from Keyword_usa_Bank_Account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.S. Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="a2ce32a8-f935-4bb6-8e96-2a5157672e2c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_usa_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_usa_Bank_Account" />
    </Pattern>
```

## <a name="us-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11387">Номер водительских прав в США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11387">U.S. driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11388">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11388">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11389">Зависит от штата.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11389">Depends on the state</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11390">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11390">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11391">зависит от состояния , например, Нью-Йорка:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11391">depends on the state - for example, New York:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11392">девять цифр, форматированные как ddd ddd ddd ddd, будут соответствовать.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11392">nine digits formatted like ddd ddd ddd will match.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11393">девять цифр, таких как dddddddd, не совпадают.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11393">nine digits like ddddddddd will not match.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11394">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11394">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11395">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11395">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11396">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11396">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11397">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11397">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11398">функция Func_new_york_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11398">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11399">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11399">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11400">обнаружено ключевое слово из списка Keyword_us_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11400">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11401">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11401">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11402">функция Func_new_york_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11402">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11403">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11403">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11404">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11404">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11405">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_us_drivers_license не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11405">No keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="dfeb356f-61cd-459e-bf0f-7c6d28b458c6 patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-individual-taxpayer-identification-number-itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11503">Индивидуальный идентификационный номер налогоплательщика США (ITIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11503">U.S. individual taxpayer identification number (ITIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11504">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11504">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11505">девять цифр, которые начинаются с "9" и содержат "7" или "8" в виде четвертой цифры, необязательно форматированные с пробелами или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11505">nine digits that start with a "9" and contain a "7" or "8" as the fourth digit, optionally formatted with spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11506">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11506">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11507">форматированный:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11507">formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11508">цифра "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11508">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11509">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11509">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11510">пространство или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11510">a space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11511">"7" или "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11511">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11512">цифру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11512">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11513">пространство или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11513">a space, or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11514">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11514">four digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11515">unformatted:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11515">unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11516">цифра "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11516">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11517">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11517">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11518">"7" или "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11518">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11519">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11519">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11520">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11520">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11521">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11521">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11522">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11522">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11523">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11523">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11524">Функция Func_formatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11524">The function Func_formatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11525">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_itin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11525">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11526">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11526">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11527">Функция Func_unformatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11527">The function Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11528">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_itin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11528">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11529">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11529">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11530">Функция Func_formatted_itin или Func_unformatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11530">The function Func_formatted_itin or Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.S. Individual Taxpayer Identification Number (ITIN) -->
    <Entity id="e55e2a32-f92d-4985-a35d-a0b269eb687b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11531">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11531">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11532">Keyword_itin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11532">Keyword_itin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11533">налогоплательщик</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11533">taxpayer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11536">itin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11536">itin</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11537">i.t.i.n.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11537">i.t.i.n.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11538">ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11538">ssn</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11541">tax payer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11541">tax payer</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11542">itins</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11542">itins</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11543">таксомоторный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11543">taxid</span></span>

## <a name="us-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11545">Номер социального обеспечения США (SSN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11545">U.S. social security number (SSN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11546">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11546">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11547">девять цифр, которые могут быть в форматированном или неформатированном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11547">nine digits, which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11548">Есть SSN выдан до середины 2011 г., он отличается строгим форматированием, при котором определенные части номера должны входить в указанные диапазоны (при этом нет контрольной суммы).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11548">If issued before mid-2011, an SSN has strong formatting where certain parts of the number must fall within certain ranges to be valid (but there's no checksum).</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11549">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11549">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11550">четыре функции искать SSNs в четырех различных шаблонов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11550">four functions look for SSNs in four different patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11551">Func_ssn находит SSN со строгим форматированием с тире или пробелами, выданные до 2011 г. (ццц-цц-цццц ИЛИ ццц цц цццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11551">Func_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11552">Func_unformatted_ssn находит SSN со строгим форматированием, выданные до 2011 г. (без форматирования в виде девяти последовательных цифр — ццццццццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11552">Func_unformatted_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11553">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn находит SSN с тире или пробелами, выданные после 2011 г. (ццц-цц-цццц ИЛИ ццц цц цццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11553">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11554">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn находит SSN без форматирования в виде девяти последовательных цифр, выданные после 2011 г. (ццццццццц).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11554">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11555">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11555">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11556">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11556">No</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11557">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11557">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11558">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11558">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11559">Функция Func_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11559">The function Func_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11560">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11560">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11561">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11561">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11562">Функция Func_unformatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11562">The function Func_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11563">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11563">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11564">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11564">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11565">Функция Func_randomized_formatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11565">The function Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11566">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11566">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11567">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11567">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11568">Функция Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11568">The function Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11569">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11569">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>


```xml
<!-- U.S. Social Security Number (SSN) -->
  <Entity id="a44669fe-0d48-453d-a9b1-2cc83f2cba77" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_formatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="55">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
  </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11570">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11570">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11571">Keyword_ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11571">Keyword_ssn</span></span>

## <a name="us--uk-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11584">U.S. / U.K.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11584">U.S. / U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11585">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11585">passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11586">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11586">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11587">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11587">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11588">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11588">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11589">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11589">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11590">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11590">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11591">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11591">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11592">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11592">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11593">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11593">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11594">функция Func_usa_uk_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11594">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11595">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11595">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11596">Найдено `Keywords_eu_passport_date` ключевое слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11596">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11597">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11597">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11598">функция Func_usa_uk_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11598">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11599">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11599">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.S. / U.K. Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="178ec42a-18b4-47cc-85c7-d62c92fd67f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11605">паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11605">passports</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11613">британский паспорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11613">british passport</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11614">uk passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11614">uk passport</span></span> 


## <a name="ukraine-passport-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11615">Внутренний паспорт Украины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11615">Ukraine passport domestic</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11616">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11616">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11617">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11617">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11618">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11618">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11619">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11619">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11620">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11620">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11621">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11621">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11622">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11622">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11623">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11623">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11624">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11624">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11625">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11625">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11626">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11626">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11627">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11627">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11628">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11628">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11629">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11629">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11630">В regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11630">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11631">Найдено ключевое слово Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11631">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport Domestic -->
      <Entity id="1817a540-221f-4459-9202-3bd78b81d803" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_ukraine_passport_domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11633">Keyword_ukraine_passport_domestic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11633">Keyword_ukraine_passport_domestic</span></span>

## <a name="ukraine-passport-international"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11640">Паспорт Украины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11640">Ukraine passport international</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11641">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11641">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11642">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11642">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11643">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11643">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11644">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11644">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11645">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11645">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11646">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11646">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11647">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11647">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11648">альфанумерный шаблон из восьми символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11648">eight-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11649">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11649">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11650">альфанумерный шаблон из восьми символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11650">eight-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11651">две буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11651">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11652">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11652">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11653">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11653">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11654">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11654">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11655">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11655">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11656">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11656">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11657">Regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11657">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11658">Ключевое слово Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11658">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport International -->
      <Entity id="cfbe032d-22e0-4f28-ab68-d66e9641f1e2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11659">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11659">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_ukraine_passport_international"></a><span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11660">Keyword_ukraine_passport_international</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11660">Keyword_ukraine_passport_international</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11661">Паспорт Украины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11661">ukraine passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11664">паспорт України</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11664">паспорт України</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a29d9-11665">номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a29d9-11665">номер паспорта</span></span>
